(44, 19, 1, '', '2018-01-04 19:19:16', 676, 2835, '4eba20a47638e4280eb8e7fa2575d882c2101742', '{\"id\":19,\"asset_id\":\"99\",\"title\":\"N\\u00famero de Etapas\",\"alias\":\"numero-de-etapas\",\"introtext\":\"<p>O campeonato ser\\u00e1 dividido em <span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><em>13 etapas<\\/em><\\/span> distribu\\u00eddas mensalmente, com in\\u00edcio em fevereiro de 2017 e t\\u00e9rmino em novembro de 2017, programadas sempre para as manh\\u00e3s de domingo no Kart\\u00f3dromo Internacional de Betim ou Kart\\u00f3dromo RBC Racing em Vespasiano.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>As datas poder\\u00e3o sofrer altera\\u00e7\\u00f5es de acordo com poss\\u00edveis necessidades do kart\\u00f3dromo desde que avisado com anteced\\u00eancia e tempo h\\u00e1bil por notifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o a todos os pilotos.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>O adiamento ou cancelamento de alguma etapa em car\\u00e1ter de urg\\u00eancia, por motivos meteorol\\u00f3gicos, t\\u00e9cnicos, etc, somente poder\\u00e1 ser determinado pelos respons\\u00e1veis do kart\\u00f3dromo no momento da corrida. Ficou firmado pela organiza\\u00e7\\u00e3o deste campeonato que <span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><em>em dias de chuva correremos sempre no tra\\u00e7ado tradicional, para minimizar os riscos de acidente<\\/em><\\/span>.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2018-01-04 19:19:16\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2018-01-04 19:18:55\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":2,\"ordering\":\"0\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"0\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0),
(49, 22, 1, '', '2018-01-04 19:23:27', 676, 4478, '10601d6f8b84307840ac5fc4be05b6db14f31452', '{\"id\":22,\"asset_id\":102,\"title\":\"Grid de Largada (2)\",\"alias\":\"grid-de-largada-2\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Todo o grid de largada<span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><em> ser\\u00e1 formado com os karts perfilados lado a lado<\\/em><\\/span>. O grid para a <span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><em>1\\u00aa etapa<\\/em><\\/span> do campeonato ser\\u00e1 formado atrav\\u00e9s de um sorteio realizado antes da corrida, em uma data e local determinado, com a presen\\u00e7a de todos os participantes ou quem tiver interesse em participar.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>O resultado final desta <span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><em>1\\u00aa etapa<\\/em><\\/span> ser\\u00e1 invertido para formar o grid da <span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><em>2\\u00aa etapa<\\/em><\\/span>. Os demais grid\'s ser\\u00e3o todos em ordem inversa \\u00e0 classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o final da etapa anterior. Todo piloto que faltar \\u00e0 uma etapa, na pr\\u00f3xima&nbsp;automaticamente ocupar\\u00e1 a ultima posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o do grid. Se mais de um faltar \\u00e0 prova, as ultimas posi\\u00e7\\u00f5es ser\\u00e3o ocupadas de acordo com a ordem de confirma\\u00e7\\u00e3o da etapa.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>A 12\\u00aa e 13\\u00aa etapas ser\\u00e3o realizadas na mesma data, sendo o grid da <span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><em>12\\u00aa etapa<\\/em><\\/span> formado na ordem real do campeonato e o grid da <span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><em>13\\u00aa etapa<\\/em><\\/span> ser\\u00e1 formada exatamente como terminou a 12\\u00aa apenas com invers\\u00e3o dos karts. Ex.: Quem chegar na 12\\u00aa etapa na primeira posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o largar\\u00e1 em primeiro lugar com o kart do ultimo colocado, o 2\\u00ba colocado largar\\u00e1 em segundo lugar com o kart do pen\\u00faltimo e assim sucessivamente. <em><span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\">S\\u00f3 poder\\u00e1 haver troca de kart caso o mesmo apresentar problemas que o impe\\u00e7am de largar (Isto ser\\u00e1 avaliado pela comiss\\u00e3o) e com isto o piloto largar\\u00e1 na ultima posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o.<\\/span><\\/em><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>A tabela do campeonato v\\u00e1lida para os crit\\u00e9rios de desempate ser\\u00e1 a (<strong>SEM DESCARTE<\\/strong>), a partir da quinta etapa a tabela de referencia ser\\u00e1 a (<strong>COM O DESCARTE<\\/strong>).<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Nas corridas os pilotos sair\\u00e3o dos boxes, dar\\u00e3o uma ou mais voltas, de acordo com decis\\u00e3o da diretoria do dia, e em seguida assumir\\u00e3o suas posi\\u00e7\\u00f5es no grid de largada lado a lado. <span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><em>Ap\\u00f3s o sorteio dos karts, o piloto s\\u00f3 poder\\u00e1 trocar o seu se o mesmo apresentar algum defeito ou situa\\u00e7\\u00e3o que o impe\\u00e7a de correr e que seja comprovado pelos mec\\u00e2nicos do kart\\u00f3dromo, al\\u00e9m de ser obrigat\\u00f3rio comunicar a um membro da diretoria.<\\/em><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":0,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2018-01-04 19:23:27\",\"modified_by\":null,\"checked_out\":null,\"checked_out_time\":null,\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":