(52, 23, 1, '', '2018-01-04 19:24:52', 676, 2677, 'd8058ae40b1c4c60fb6cdac5963db07ef23a7422', '{\"id\":23,\"asset_id\":\"103\",\"title\":\"Convidados ou Participantes Extras\",\"alias\":\"convidados-ou-participantes-extras\",\"introtext\":\"<p>De acordo com os votos de 24 participantes ficou determinado que a partir de 20 de mar\\u00e7o de 2009, todo piloto que n\\u00e3o esteja inscrito no campeonato e participar de uma corrida, ter\\u00e1 sua posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o ignorada na pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o do campeonato e sua posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o ocupada pelo piloto participante que estiver logo ap\\u00f3s. <span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><em>Ficou tamb\\u00e9m estabelecido que n\\u00e3o haver\\u00e1 a participa\\u00e7\\u00e3o de\\u00a0<\\/em><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-size: 12.16px;\\\"><span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><em>convidados na ultima rodada (12\\u00aa e 13\\u00aa etapas)<\\/em><\\/span>. Nesta ultima rodada o piloto desclassificado na 12\\u00aa ser\\u00e1 penalizado e largar\\u00e1 na ultima posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o do grid al\\u00e9m de ficar com a pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o igual a (zero).<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2018-01-04 19:24:52\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2018-01-04 19:24:13\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\"