(70, 15, 1, '', '2018-01-19 13:08:08', 676, 2386, 'fd9d12f241fe5b3a956000bbbc46247f73acbf85', '{\"id\":15,\"asset_id\":\"95\",\"title\":\"Premia\\u00e7\\u00e3o\",\"alias\":\"premiacao\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Ser\\u00e3o premiados com medalhas em todas as etapas os cinco primeiros colocados. Ao final do campeonato, ser\\u00e3o premiados com trof\\u00e9us os quinze primeiros colocados. Tamb\\u00e9m ser\\u00e3o premiadas com trof\\u00e9us as cinco primeiras equipes do campeonato, considerando o desempenho do ano todo e obedecendo as regras de desempate do torneio.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>As vagas para a <span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\">Copa dos campe\\u00f5es<\\/span> ser\\u00e3o para os cinco primeiros na coloca\\u00e7\\u00e3o geral do campeonato ou&nbsp;em n\\u00fameros estipulados pela Akamig para cada campeonato.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2018-01-19 13:08:08\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2018-01-19 13:07:00\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_