(76, 16, 1, '', '2018-01-19 14:03:54', 676, 3570, '1276d70f5e20e7d045f851da093393d13d8c50a1', '{\"id\":16,\"asset_id\":\"96\",\"title\":\"Pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o do Campeonato\",\"alias\":\"pontuacao-do-campeonato\",\"introtext\":\"<div style=\\\"display: table; margin: auto;\\\">\\r\\n<p>01\\u00ba &nbsp;- 33 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 09\\u00ba - 22 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 17\\u00ba - 14 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 25\\u00ba - 06 pontos<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>02\\u00ba &nbsp;- 30 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 10\\u00ba - 21 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 18\\u00ba - 13 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 26\\u00ba - 05 pontos<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>03\\u00ba &nbsp;- 28 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 11\\u00ba - 20 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 19\\u00ba - 12 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 27\\u00ba - 04 pontos<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>04\\u00ba &nbsp;- 27 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 12\\u00ba - 19 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 20\\u00ba - 11 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 28\\u00ba - 03 pontos<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>05\\u00ba &nbsp;- 26 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 13\\u00ba - 18 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 21\\u00ba - 10 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 29\\u00ba - 02 pontos<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>06\\u00ba &nbsp;- 25 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 14\\u00ba - 17 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 22\\u00ba - 09 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 30\\u00ba - 01 ponto<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>07\\u00ba &nbsp;- 24 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 15\\u00ba - 16 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 23\\u00ba - 08 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 31\\u00ba - Zero<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>08\\u00ba &nbsp;- 23 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 16\\u00ba - 15 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 24\\u00ba - 07 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 32\\u00ba - Zero<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<p>Ainda ganhar\\u00e3o pontos os cinco pilotos que fizerem as melhores voltas da prova da seguinte forma: O primeiro ganhar\\u00e1 1 ponto e os demais que fizerem as 2\\u00aa, 3\\u00aa, 4\\u00aa e 5\\u00aa ganhar\\u00e3o 0,5 ponto cada um.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2018-01-19 14:03:54\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2018-01-19 14:01:57\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":5,\"orde