(77, 22, 1, '', '2018-01-19 14:09:29', 676, 2935, '50a1573ad7158fa734a4b7c7dabdc527526bed0f', '{\"id\":22,\"asset_id\":\"102\",\"title\":\"Desempate na Classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o do Campeonato\",\"alias\":\"desempate-na-classificacao-do-campeonato\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Ser\\u00e3o adotados os seguintes crit\\u00e9rios para o desempate, 1\\u00ba - Maior numero de vit\\u00f3rias, 2\\u00ba - Maior numero de segundo lugar, 3\\u00ba - Maior numero de terceiro lugar, 4\\u00ba - maior numero de quarto lugar, 5\\u00ba - Maior numero de quinto lugar, 6\\u00ba - Maior numero de \\\"Volta mais r\\u00e1pida\\\", 7\\u00ba - Menor numero de faltas, 8\\u00ba - Sorteio. Ao final do campeonato todos os pilotos ter\\u00e3o direito a descartar 2 resultados. Sendo assim ser\\u00e3o descartados as piores coloca\\u00e7\\u00f5es em prova ou mesmo uma aus\\u00eancia. J\\u00e1 as equipes ir\\u00e3o descartar a pior pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o <span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><em>por somat\\u00f3ria da etapa<\\/em><\\/span>. Por exemplo se em <em>uma etapa o piloto A fez venceu e fez 33 pontos e o piloto B chegou em ultimo e fez 01 ponto, a somat\\u00f3ria da equipe ficou em 34 pontos<\\/em>. <em><span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\">N\\u00e3o ser\\u00e1 permitido descartar uma pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o igual a (zero), se esta for proveniente de uma desclassifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o.<\\/span><\\/em><\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2018-01-19 14:09:29\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2018-01-19 14:05:35\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":3,\"ordering\":\"5\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"4\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0);
