(83, 20, 1, '', '2018-02-06 20:13:37', 676, 2836, '6aeee7824f152153c0fc6429766c94310dbdc9e3', '{\"id\":20,\"asset_id\":\"100\",\"title\":\"Inscri\\u00e7\\u00e3o\",\"alias\":\"inscricao\",\"introtext\":\"<p>O pagamento da inscri\\u00e7\\u00e3o que ir\\u00e1 confirmar a presen\\u00e7a do piloto no campeonato, dever\\u00e1 ser feito entre os dias <span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\">14 e 18 de dezembro de 2017<\\/span>. Todo piloto inscrito dever\\u00e1 pagar a<span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><em><strong> taxa \\u00fanica de R$250,00 (duzentos e cinquenta reais) na data estipulada e este valor n\\u00e3o ser\\u00e1 devolvido caso o piloto abandone o campeonato<\\/strong><\\/em><\\/span>. Cada participante receber\\u00e1 uma camiseta comemorativa do evento e ter\\u00e1 direito a participar da festa de encerramento levando um(a) acompanhante alem de concorrer aos pr\\u00eamios previstos neste regulamento.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Ser\\u00e3o formadas equipes com dois participantes em escolha livre ou se n\\u00e3o quiserem, ser\\u00e1 escolhida pela organiza\\u00e7\\u00e3o. Esta equipe ter\\u00e1 que permanecer por todo o campeonato, n\\u00e3o podendo haver mudan\\u00e7as de algum participante migrando para outra equipe, mesmo se houver abandono por um dos membros.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2018-02-06 20:13:37\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2018-02-06 20:12:21\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":6,\"ordering\":\"7\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"32\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0),
(84, 15, 1, '', '2018-02-06 20:14:31', 676, 2382, 'd36623fefb5e91255a097116a3ff0c99bb08edf6', '{\"id\":15,\"asset_id\":\"95\",\"title\":\"Premia\\u00e7\\u00e3o\",\"alias\":\"premiacao\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Ser\\u00e3o premiados com medalhas em todas as etapas os cinco primeiros colocados. Ao final do campeonato, ser\\u00e3o premiados com trof\\u00e9us os quinze primeiros colocados. Tamb\\u00e9m ser\\u00e3o premiadas com trof\\u00e9us as cinco primeiras equipes do campeonato, considerando o desempenho do ano todo e obedecendo as regras de desempate do torneio.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>As vagas para a <span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\">Copa dos campe\\u00f5es<\\/span> ser\\u00e3o para os cinco primeiros na coloca\\u00e7\\u00e3o geral do campeonato ou em n\\u00fameros estipulados pela Akamig para cada campeonato.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2018-02-06 20:14:31\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2018-02-06 20:13:53\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_categ