(85, 19, 1, '', '2018-02-06 20:15:56', 676, 2841, '8df39a4e7afc3d2369e21c8c842114f00d4a7b84', '{\"id\":19,\"asset_id\":\"99\",\"title\":\"N\\u00famero de Etapas\",\"alias\":\"numero-de-etapas\",\"introtext\":\"<p>O campeonato ser\\u00e1 dividido em <span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><em><strong>13 etapas<\\/strong><\\/em><\\/span> distribu\\u00eddas mensalmente, com in\\u00edcio em 04 de fevereiro de 2018 e t\\u00e9rmino em 25 de novembro de 2018, programadas sempre para as manh\\u00e3s de domingo no Kartodromo Internacional de Betim ou Kartodromo RBC Racing em Vespasiano.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>As datas poder\\u00e3o sofrer altera\\u00e7\\u00f5es de acordo com poss\\u00edveis necessidades do kart\\u00f3dromo desde que avisado com anteced\\u00eancia e tempo h\\u00e1bil por notifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o a todos os pilotos.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>O adiamento ou cancelamento de alguma etapa em car\\u00e1ter de urg\\u00eancia, por motivos meteorol\\u00f3gicos, t\\u00e9cnicos, etc, somente poder\\u00e1 ser determinado pelos respons\\u00e1veis do kartodromo no momento da corrida. Ficou firmado pela organiza\\u00e7\\u00e3o deste campeonato que <span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\">em dias de chuva correremos sempre no tra\\u00e7ado tradicional, para minimizar os riscos de acidente<\\/span>.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2018-02-06 20:15:56\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2018-02-06 20:14:45\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"t