(88, 17, 1, '', '2018-02-06 20:27:56', 676, 2758, '78189415d8108f139cff7fb8c13233b67cffeaf4', '{\"id\":17,\"asset_id\":\"97\",\"title\":\"Peso do Piloto\",\"alias\":\"peso-do-piloto\",\"introtext\":\"<p>O peso base para todos os pilotos ser\\u00e1 de 95Kg e caso n\\u00e3o atinja ser\\u00e1 acrescido de lastros oferecido pelo kartodromo ou colocados dentro do macac\\u00e3o. N\\u00e3o ser\\u00e1 mais permitido nenhum tipo de lastro aparente, agarrado ao corpo ou no kart. <span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><em><strong>N\\u00e3o haver\\u00e1 toler\\u00e2ncia nenhuma e qualquer peso abaixo ter\\u00e1 de ser lastreado<\\/strong><\\/em><\\/span>. O piloto que precisar trocar o kart durante a prova dever\\u00e1 levar o lastro ou ser\\u00e1 desclassificado, ficando com a pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o igual a (zero). Toda pesagem ser\\u00e1 feita por dois diretores ou designados pelos mesmos depois da prova e <span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><strong><em>todos os pilotos dever\\u00e3o ser pesados<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/span>, bem como o lastro de seus karts vistoriados. Ap\\u00f3s a corrida nenhum piloto poder\\u00e1 sair da \\u00e1rea de pesagem e nem consumir nenhum tipo de liquido.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2018-02-06 20:27:56\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2018-02-06 20:22:43\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":4,\"ordering\":\"10\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"36\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0),
(89, 23, 1, '', '2018-02-06 20:29:42', 676, 2487, 'd6315c84919f2a9b3352933c619a6e230c99c7c4', '{\"id\":23,\"asset_id\":\"103\",\"title\":\"Convidados ou Participantes Extras\",\"alias\":\"convidados-ou-participantes-extras\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Este ano devido ao grande numero de pilotos efetivos, <span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\">n\\u00e3o aceitaremos convidados<\\/span> a menos que seja necess\\u00e1rio completar o grid com o numero m\\u00ednimo de pilotos estipulado pelo kartodromo. <span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><em><strong>Ficou tamb\\u00e9m estabelecido que n\\u00e3o haver\\u00e1 a participa\\u00e7\\u00e3o de convidados na ultima rodada (12\\u00aa e 13\\u00aa etapas)<\\/strong><\\/em><\\/span>. Nesta ultima rodada o piloto desclassificado na 12\\u00aa ser\\u00e1 penalizado e largar\\u00e1 na ultima posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o do grid al\\u00e9m de ficar com a pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o igual a (zero).<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2018-02-06 20:29:42\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2018-02-06 20:28:07\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"inf