(91, 25, 1, '', '2018-02-06 20:33:15', 676, 2844, 'e8aa0f661ba62cdf6cf797a7980e71f087c9fc8d', '{\"id\":25,\"asset_id\":\"105\",\"title\":\"Comunica\\u00e7\\u00e3o\",\"alias\":\"comunicacao\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Todo participante ter\\u00e1 o calend\\u00e1rio de todas as corridas a serem realizadas no ano, expostas no site <span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\">www.masterkart.com.br<\\/span> para que possam agendar e n\\u00e3o terem motivos de aus\\u00eancias por esquecimento ou falta de conhecimento, mesmo assim, receber\\u00e3o emails nos dias que antecederem a corrida avisando a data, hora e local do evento para que possam se lembrar e, assim, confirmarem suas presen\\u00e7as. Toda confirma\\u00e7\\u00e3o dever\\u00e1 ser feita at\\u00e9 as 18:00hs da quinta feira que anteceder a prova atrav\\u00e9s de email ou mesmo por mensagem texto pelo telefone celular do Cadu. <span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><strong><em>Todos os emails de confirma\\u00e7\\u00e3o, dever\\u00e3o ser respondidos, mesmo se o piloto n\\u00e3o puder comparecer, para sabermos o numero de participantes e que outro possa assumir sua vaga caso o numero seja insuficiente. Quem n\\u00e3o responder ser\\u00e1 penalizado com a perda de 02 pontos na contagem geral.<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2018-02-06 20:33:15\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2018-02-06 20:32:04\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":4,\"ordering\":\"2\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"18\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0),
(92, 18, 1, '', '2018-02-06 20:40:11', 676, 5863, 'd188c9407d1a64fee5b9c719d37cca7af41be24a', '{\"id\":18,\"asset_id\":\"98\",\"title\":\"Penalidades\",\"alias\":\"penalidades\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Primeiramente ser\\u00e1 obedecido este regulamento e em casos omissos a decis\\u00e3o ser\\u00e1 dada pela comiss\\u00e3o. O piloto que <strong><span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><em>confirmar sua presen\\u00e7a e n\\u00e3o comparecer, perder\\u00e1 2 pontos<\\/em><\\/span><\\/strong> na somat\\u00f3ria de sua pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o geral. <span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><strong><em>O piloto que n\\u00e3o confirmar sua presen\\u00e7a at\\u00e9 a data e hora estabelecida<\\/em><\\/strong><em><strong>&nbsp;perder\\u00e1 2 pontos<\\/strong><\\/em><\\/span>, mas poder\\u00e1 participar da etapa, na ultima posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o, n\\u00e3o contado os pilotos convidados se houverem.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Ao final de cada etapa a pesagem de todos os pilotos \\u00e9 obrigat\\u00f3ria, n\\u00e3o podendo o mesmo sair do local da corrida e nem beber algum tipo de l\\u00edquido. Quem esquecer de pesar, estiver abaixo do peso m\\u00ednimo de (95 quilos) ou mesmo o seu kart n\\u00e3o tiver com o peso estabelecido, <span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><em><strong>ser\\u00e1 desclassificado, ficando com a pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o igual a (zero)<\\/strong><\\/em><\\/span>.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><em><strong>Todo participante dever\\u00e1 chegar 30 minutos antes do inicio da largada ou perder\\u00e1 2 pontos na contagem geral. Ser\\u00e1 usado como hor\\u00e1rio referencia a R\\u00e1dio Itatiaia.<\\/strong><\\/em><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><em><strong>Todo participante que n\\u00e3o estiver trajando a camiseta oficial do campeonato de 2018 perder\\u00e1 2 pontos na contagem geral.<\\/strong><\\/em><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><em><strong>Todo participante que tiver mais de um ter\\u00e7o de falta do total de corridas do campeonato, sem justificativa, poder\\u00e1 ficar de fora do pr\\u00f3ximo campeonato, ficando a julgamento da diretoria.<\\/strong><\\/em><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><em><strong>\\u00c9 proibido empurrar. Durante a corrida ficar\\u00e1 a encargo do diretor de prova avaliar e punir quem cometer esta infra\\u00e7\\u00e3o, podendo os dois pilotos serem punidos.<\\/strong><\\/em><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00c9 terminantemente proibido qualquer piloto, ap\\u00f3s a corrida, procurar, reclamar ou questionar a decis\\u00e3o do diretor de prova. Toda e qualquer reclama\\u00e7\\u00e3o dever\\u00e1 ser encaminhada imediatamente ap\\u00f3s a corrida, aos membros da diretoria do MasterKart, m\\u00ednimo de dois, acompanhado de v\\u00eddeo pessoal para basear a sua reclama\\u00e7\\u00e3o \\/ defesa.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Ser\\u00e3o acatadas todas as puni\\u00e7\\u00f5es dadas pela dire\\u00e7\\u00e3o do kartodromo <span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><em><strong>com a perda de 5 (cinco) pontos<\\/strong><\\/em><\\/span> e sem direito a reclama\\u00e7\\u00f5es verbais. Caso o piloto j\\u00e1 seja reincidente, a<span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><em><strong> penalidade ser\\u00e1 de 10 (dez) pontos<\\/strong><\\/em><\\/span>. Se houver alguma prova em v\\u00eddeo que comprove algum equivoco por parte do kartodromo o piloto dever\\u00e1 encaminhar imediatamente a um membro da comiss\\u00e3o e se a diretoria achar justo, este ter\\u00e1 seus pontos devolvidos. <span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><em><strong>Ser\\u00e1 considerado falta grave, perdendo 10 pontos, o piloto que agredir ou ofender outro participante ou funcion\\u00e1rio do kartodromo e ser\\u00e1 punido de acordo com decis\\u00e3o da diretoria.<\\/strong><\\/em><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Todas as penalidades julgadas, ou impostas pelo kartodromo, ir\\u00e3o valer tanto para pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o quanto para o p\\u00f3dio (fotografias) hist\\u00f3rico de corridas. O v\\u00eddeo valer\\u00e1 como prova, <span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\">apenas para retirar alguma penalidade imposta, ficando isento o kartodromo<\\/span> se assim for o entendimento da diretoria, <span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\">n\\u00e3o valendo para criar uma penalidade<\\/span> que por ventura n\\u00e3o tenha sido dada pelo kartodromo.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2018-02-06 20:40:11\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2018-02-06 20:33:30\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":4,\"ordering\":\"9\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"32\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0);
