(94, 24, 1, '', '2018-02-06 20:43:14', 676, 2263, '48f2b953dd1278deff0633dc5a3d8a006b4e5b68', '{\"id\":24,\"asset_id\":\"104\",\"title\":\"Contatos\",\"alias\":\"contatos\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Todos os resultados, fotos, not\\u00edcias e qualquer tipo de contato ser\\u00e1 feito atrav\\u00e9s deste site<strong> www.masterkart.com.br<\\/strong> , por e-mail <strong>diretoria@masterkart.com.br<\\/strong> e ainda criaremos uma comunica\\u00e7\\u00e3o atrav\\u00e9s do WhatsApp onde informaremos desde alguma mudan\\u00e7a vinda da dire\\u00e7\\u00e3o do kart\\u00f3dromo como as datas e hor\\u00e1rios das provas com bastante anteced\\u00eancia ou at\\u00e9 mesmo uma solicita\\u00e7\\u00e3o de voto.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2018-02-06 20:43:14\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2018-02-06 20:42:13\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\