(115, 19, 1, '', '2023-02-08 18:43:09', 676, 3726, 'c9438a0257aaab385af3e75825a899743a509e40', '{\"id\":19,\"asset_id\":\"99\",\"title\":\"PREMIA\\u00c7\\u00c3O DO CAMPEONATO\",\"alias\":\"premiacao-do-campeonato\",\"introtext\":\"<p>A festa de confraterniza\\u00e7\\u00e3o, est\\u00e1 prevista para ser realizada em<strong><span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"> 03 de dezembro 2023<\\/span><\\/strong>, ap\\u00f3s a \\u00faltima corrida do ano, conforme as vezes passadas. Esta, por sua vez, ser\\u00e1 confirmada antes da \\u00faltima corrida, onde ser\\u00e3o entregues os trof\\u00e9us de pilotos, equipes e de participa\\u00e7\\u00e3o sendo:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;01 (um) trof\\u00e9u para os 05 (cinco) melhores pilotos da categoria FAST.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;01 (um) trof\\u00e9u para os 05 (cinco) melhores pilotos da categoria FURIOUS.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;01 (um) trof\\u00e9u para cada piloto das 03 (tr\\u00eas) melhores equipes de cada categoria.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;01 (um) trof\\u00e9u para o campe\\u00e3o do primeiro e segundo semestre.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Crit\\u00e9rios de desempate na Classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o por pilotos:&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;1\\u00b0 - Maior n\\u00famero de vit\\u00f3rias do piloto no campeonato;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;2\\u00b0 - Maior n\\u00famero de 2\\u00aa posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o do piloto no campeonato;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;3\\u00b0 - Maior n\\u00famero de 3\\u00aa posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o do piloto no campeonato, e assim sucessivamente.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Crit\\u00e9rios de desempate na Classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o das equipes:&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;1\\u00b0 - Maior n\\u00famero de vit\\u00f3rias de pilotos da equipe no campeonato;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;2\\u00b0 - Maior n\\u00famero de 2\\u00aa posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o de pilotos da equipe no campeonato;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;3\\u00b0-Maior n\\u00famero de 3\\u00aa posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o de pilotos da equipe no campeonato, e assim sucessivamente.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Os trof\\u00e9us da Categoria FAST e FURIOUS a serem entregues nas etapas constar\\u00e3o a categoria e a Coloca\\u00e7\\u00e3o do piloto: Campe\\u00e3o, Vice-campe\\u00e3o, Terceiro, Quarto e Quinto lugares.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-02-08 18:43:09\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2023-02-08 18:40:11\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":5,\"ordering\":\"11\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"350\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0),
(116, 15, 1, '', '2023-02-08 18:45:49', 676, 4254, 'ab6c743a0a4c7f99b11e7b75b10cb34651acc619', '{\"id\":15,\"asset_id\":\"95\",\"title\":\"Premia\\u00e7\\u00e3o\",\"alias\":\"premiacao\",\"introtext\":\"<p>6.1) No dia da corrida os pilotos devem chegar ao kart\\u00f3dromo no m\\u00ednimo com 30 (trinta) minutos de anteced\\u00eancia ao hor\\u00e1rio previsto para o in\\u00edcio da corrida. 6.2) Est\\u00e1 previsto o in\\u00edcio do briefing da corrida com 30 minutos antes da largada. 6.2.1) O piloto deve estar inscrito na corrida at\\u00e9 o final da pesagem e sorteio dos KARTS. Quem chegar ap\\u00f3s o in\\u00edcio do briefing, mesmo que esteja nas depend\\u00eancias do kart\\u00f3dromo, ir\\u00e1 largar da \\u00faltima posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o de sua categoria. Caso mais de 1 piloto se atrasar, a posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o ser\\u00e1 pela ordem de chegada a partir da \\u00faltima posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o do grid. 6.3) Os Karts ser\\u00e3o definidos por SORTEIO no briefing que antecede a corrida. O sorteio ser\\u00e1 realizado pelo diretor de prova juntamente com a equipe do kart\\u00f3dromo. 6.4) O grid ser\\u00e1 montado na ordem inversa da posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o de classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o do campeonato, conforme a categoria. E poder\\u00e1 come\\u00e7ar tanto com os pilotos da categoria FAST, quanto com os pilotos da categoria FURIOUS. 6.4.1) o grid das categorias Fast e Furious na primeira corrida (janeiro) ser\\u00e1 definido por tomada de tempo de cinco minutos. 6.4.2) A largada ser\\u00e1 em movimento e em fila DUPLA. 6.4.3) Durante as voltas de alinhamento e largada \\u00e9 proibido a ultrapassagem. A exce\\u00e7\\u00e3o \\u00e9: defeito, sa\\u00edda de pista, derrapagem ou indica\\u00e7\\u00e3o da organiza\\u00e7\\u00e3o do kart\\u00f3dromo. 6.4.4) Durante a volta de alinhamento, o piloto deve manter sua posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o LADO A LADO com o piloto de refer\\u00eancia ao seu lado e, por conseguinte, manter dist\\u00e2ncia de seguran\\u00e7a com os pilotos a sua frente. Caso por alguma imper\\u00edcia o piloto vir a derrapar, rodar e\\/ou sair da pista com o kart, dever\\u00e1 aguardar o fim do pelot\\u00e3o de largada. 6.5) N\\u00e3o ser\\u00e1 permitido ao piloto, em hip\\u00f3tese alguma, fazer qualquer tipo de regulagem, ou altera\\u00e7\\u00e3o no kart que o piloto receber no sorteio tanto com o kart parado quanto em movimento. A \\u00fanica regulagem autorizada \\u00e9 a da posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o de banco, qualquer outra, somente poder\\u00e1 ser efetuada pelos mec\\u00e2nicos da pista; Exceto se houver algum problema no kart. 6.6) O piloto poder\\u00e1 substituir o seu kart, obrigatoriamente, por outro kart sorteado pelo kart\\u00f3dromo, e ir\\u00e1 largar na \\u00faltima posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o do grid.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-02-08 18:45:49\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2023-02-08 18:45:31\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":7,\"ordering\":\"15\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"336\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0),
