(120, 21, 1, '', '2023-02-08 19:10:34', 676, 5984, '8a341439ab914fb67d19803d3132a7e8a073c916', '{\"id\":21,\"asset_id\":\"101\",\"title\":\"PUNI\\u00c7\\u00d5ES\",\"alias\":\"punicoes\",\"introtext\":\"<p>As puni\\u00e7\\u00f5es com perda de pontos ser\\u00e3o aplicadas no somat\\u00f3rio da pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o da classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o dos pilotos e equipes, e n\\u00e3o ser\\u00e3o retiradas em caso de o resultado da etapa ser usado na classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o como descarte.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>O piloto que n\\u00e3o se apresentar utilizando a camisa oficial do SPEEDKART, receber\\u00e1 a puni\\u00e7\\u00e3o de 5 pontos.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Haver\\u00e1 uma puni\\u00e7\\u00e3o de 05 (cinco) pontos, em cada prova que o piloto correr sem a devida identifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o; para n\\u00e3o perder os pontos os pilotos dever\\u00e3o se identificar com nome VIS\\u00cdVEL no macac\\u00e3o, capacete ou com a camisa do SPEEDKART.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>O piloto que derrubar os cones colocados para sinalizar a passagem da largada ou instalados para sinaliza\\u00e7\\u00e3o na pista receber\\u00e1 uma puni\\u00e7\\u00e3o de 5 (cinco) pontos.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>O piloto que receber uma advert\\u00eancia do kart\\u00f3dromo por imprud\\u00eancia e\\/ou conduta antiesportiva, ser\\u00e1 penalizado em 5 (cinco) posi\\u00e7\\u00f5es no resultado da corrida, que ser\\u00e1 aplicada imediatamente ap\\u00f3s a realiza\\u00e7\\u00e3o da corrida, n\\u00e3o havendo possibilidade de recurso para esse tipo de penalidade.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Para condutas antidesportivas que n\\u00e3o foram registradas pelo kart\\u00f3dromo, por\\u00e9m capturadas por c\\u00e2meras na bateria, esta ser\\u00e1 analisada pela comiss\\u00e3o disciplinar para defini\\u00e7\\u00e3o de poss\\u00edvel puni\\u00e7\\u00e3o. Para esse caso, o prazo m\\u00e1ximo ser\\u00e1 de at\\u00e9 05 (cinco) dias ap\\u00f3s a corrida. Caso confirmado, o piloto infrator receber\\u00e1 uma puni\\u00e7\\u00e3o de 5(cinco) posi\\u00e7\\u00f5es no resultado da corrida. Caso o piloto que causou a infra\\u00e7\\u00e3o tenha se beneficiado e subido ao p\\u00f3dio, esse, por sua vez, dever\\u00e1 devolver o trof\\u00e9u que ser\\u00e1 encaminhado a quem de direito.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Caso algum piloto se sinta prejudicado na corrida por algum oponente este, por sua vez, dever\\u00e1 procurar a comiss\\u00e3o disciplinar e relatar o ocorrido, registrando a reclama\\u00e7\\u00e3o formalmente por escrito (via whatsapp ou e-mail). A comiss\\u00e3o ir\\u00e1 analisar a reclama\\u00e7\\u00e3o, consultando os envolvidos e os poss\\u00edveis testemunhos de outros pilotos. Caso confirmado, ser\\u00e1 aplicado a puni\\u00e7\\u00e3o de 05 (cinco) pontos ao piloto infrator.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>A reclama\\u00e7\\u00e3o deve ser enviada direto ao whatsapp da comiss\\u00e3o, n\\u00e3o deve ser postado no grupo do Speed kart 2023&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>O piloto que queimar a largada, realizar a ultrapassagem ou sair da linha antes da passagem pela linha de partida ser\\u00e1 punido com 05 (cinco) posi\\u00e7\\u00f5es no resultado da corrida.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>O piloto que for flagrado saindo com as 4 rodas para fora das faixas de delimita\\u00e7\\u00e3o da pista, para obter vantagem em ultrapassagens, ser\\u00e1 penalizado em 5 (cinco) posi\\u00e7\\u00f5es no resultado da corrida. Exceto quando o kart da frente estiver rodando ou danificado.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>N\\u00e3o \\u00e9 permitido ao piloto ficar mudando de faixa para impedir a ultrapassagem. \\u00c9 permitido o m\\u00e1ximo 2 mudan\\u00e7as de faixa, sendo a \\u00faltima se for necess\\u00e1rio para tomada de curva. O piloto flagrado nesta conduta ser\\u00e1 punido com 05 (cinco) posi\\u00e7\\u00f5es no resultado da corrida.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Por ter o esp\\u00edrito amig\\u00e1vel e saud\\u00e1vel, n\\u00e3o ser\\u00e3o toleradas condutas agressivas ou ofensas verbais. Ser\\u00e1 aplicado um a puni\\u00e7\\u00e3o de 60 (sessenta) pontos para cada ocorr\\u00eancia. Em casos extremos, com concord\\u00e2ncia de maioria simples dos pilotos, os envolvidos ser\\u00e3o convidados a sa\\u00edrem do campeonato. Sem direito a qualquer ressarcimento.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Nas etapas de endurance ser\\u00e3o aplicadas as regras do kartodormo;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #ff0000;\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/rbcracing.com.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/11\\/REGULAMENTO-ENDURANCE-210KM.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" style=\\\"color: #ff0000;\\\">LINK<\\/a><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-02-08 19:10:34\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2023-02-08 19:10:04\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":8,\"ordering\":\"9\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"458\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0),
(121, 14, 1, '', '2023-02-08 19:12:26', 676, 2729, 'a445bd10c40a2ea49860917c477668598a784aab', '{\"id\":14,\"asset_id\":\"94\",\"title\":\"DISPOSI\\u00c7\\u00d5ES GERAIS\",\"alias\":\"disposicoes-gerais\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Em caso de quebra durante a volta de apresenta\\u00e7\\u00e3o antes do posicionamento no grid, o piloto poder\\u00e1 trocar seu kart pelo primeiro dispon\\u00edvel da lista de reservas previamente sorteada desde que este defeito seja comprovado pelos mec\\u00e2nicos do kart\\u00f3dromo e comunicado a um membro da diretoria. <span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><strong><em>Neste caso o piloto trocar\\u00e1 o kart e manter\\u00e1 a posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o no grid<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/span>.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><em>Sem motivos aparentes ou defeitos comprovados pelos mec\\u00e2nicos, o piloto s\\u00f3 poder\\u00e1 trocar o kart depois da bandeirada de largada e ap\\u00f3s dar pelo menos uma volta na pista ou ser\\u00e1 desclassificado da prova, ficando com a pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o igual a (zero), se o ato for detectado por algum piloto participante e levado ao conhecimento da diretoria.<\\/em><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-02-08 19:12:26\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2023-02-08 19:12:14\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":6,\"ordering\":\"16\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"335\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0),
(122, 14, 1, '', '2023-02-08 19:47:23', 676, 5853, 'ec70fdcf8862ab782f3fbb3eb25cf49d8d751dd6', '{\"id\":14,\"asset_id\":\"94\",\"title\":\"DISPOSI\\u00c7\\u00d5ES GERAIS\",\"alias\":\"disposicoes-gerais\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Os candidatos interessados em participar do campeonato dever\\u00e3o solicitar a inscri\\u00e7\\u00e3o pr\\u00e9via no site do campeonato SPEEDKART \\u2013 <span style=\\\"color: #ff0000;\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/speedkartclub.net\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" style=\\\"color: #ff0000;\\\">www.SPEEDKARTclub.net<\\/a><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>O campeonato ter\\u00e1, no m\\u00e1ximo, 40 pilotos por categoria. A ordem de inscri\\u00e7\\u00e3o ser\\u00e1 pela data e hora da solicita\\u00e7\\u00e3o.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Ap\\u00f3s esgotado o n\\u00famero de vagas, ser\\u00e1 aberto a lista de espera em ordem idem acima.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>A confirma\\u00e7\\u00e3o da inscri\\u00e7\\u00e3o ser\\u00e1 feita ap\\u00f3s efetuado \\u00e0 comiss\\u00e3o organizadora, o pagamento a do valor da inscri\\u00e7\\u00e3o do campeonato.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Ser\\u00e1 cobrada de cada piloto uma taxa de inscri\\u00e7\\u00e3o para a temporada 2023 no valor de R$550,00 (QUINHENTOS E CINQUENTA REAIS). Esses valores poder\\u00e3o ser pagos da seguinte forma:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;A vista, via transfer\\u00eancia banc\\u00e1ria ou PIX, at\\u00e9 o dia 10\\/01\\/2023 com desconto, ficando o valor em R$499,00 (QUATROCENTOS E NOVENTA E NOVE REAIS).<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;Parcelamento em 5x, sem juros, via transfer\\u00eancia banc\\u00e1ria ou PIX, com vencimento das parcelas em 10\\/01\\/2023, 10\\/02\\/2023, 10\\/03\\/2023, 10\\/04\\/2023 e 10\\/05\\/2023 no valor de R$110,00 cada parcela.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;Parcelamento em 10x, com acr\\u00e9scimo, via Cart\\u00e3o de Credito na plataforma MERCADO PAGO no valor de R$59,90 cada.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>O valor da primeira parcela ou integral da inscri\\u00e7\\u00e3o poder\\u00e1 ser feito at\\u00e9 o dia 10\\/01\\/2023 por transfer\\u00eancia banc\\u00e1ria nos dados abaixo:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #ff0000;\\\">Banco Original (212) <\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #ff0000;\\\">Ag: 0001<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #ff0000;\\\"> CC 135186-9<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #ff0000;\\\"> Titular: Islander da Silveira Franco Lisboa<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #ff0000;\\\"> CPF: 011.891.516-93 <\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #ff0000;\\\">PIX <a href=\\\"mailto:islander@hotmail.com.br\\\" style=\\\"color: #ff0000;\\\">islander@hotmail.com.br<\\/a><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Para quem optar por fazer o pagamento parcelado, o vencimento das demais parcelas se dar\\u00e1 no dia 10 de cada m\\u00eas.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>O piloto que estiver inadimplente com o pagamento da inscri\\u00e7\\u00e3o do campeonato n\\u00e3o ter\\u00e1 seus pontos computados na classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o do campeonato.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>A inscri\\u00e7\\u00f5es que ocorrerem ap\\u00f3s a primeira Etapa ter\\u00e3o o valor integral, sem desconto, mesmo para o pagamento a vista.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Os valores ser\\u00e3o utilizados para o pagamento das seguintes despesas:&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Uma camisa e um bon\\u00e9 oficial do SPEEDKART.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Poder\\u00e1 ser adquirido por quem desejar, camisas extras do campeonato SPEEDKART. O custo estimado da avulsa \\u00e9 R$ 80,00 cada (Masculina, Feminina ou Infantil).<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Trof\\u00e9us de premia\\u00e7\\u00e3o das etapas e do final do ano;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Festa de confraterniza\\u00e7\\u00e3o para o piloto (com direito a um acompanhante adulto e at\\u00e9 duas crian\\u00e7as de at\\u00e9 12 anos);&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Para festa do final do campeonato, caso o piloto desejar mais de 1 acompanhante, ser\\u00e1 cobrado um valor adicional a ser estipulado em Novembro\\/23. Crian\\u00e7as de at\\u00e9 05 anos de idade n\\u00e3o pagam.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Para esclarecimento de d\\u00favidas sobre esse regulamento, favor entrar em contato com a comiss\\u00e3o organizadora que \\u00e9 formada pelos seguintes membros:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Leo Marx<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Islander Lisboa (Dinho)<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Marcio Vasconcelos<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Chico<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Fernando Mota<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Este regulamento estrar\\u00e1 em vigor no dia 01\\/01\\/2023 e ter\\u00e1 sua vig\\u00eancia at\\u00e9 o final da temporada.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-02-08 19:47:23\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2023-02-08 19:12:26\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":7,\"ordering\":\"16\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"335\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0),
(123, 93, 1, '', '2023-02-09 18:11:21', 676, 2367, '5292c724310314e036f824554e94b94b47e8a66a', '{\"id\":93,\"asset_id\":\"446\",\"title\":\"GERAL\",\"alias\":\"geral\",\"introtext\":\"<p>&nbsp;1.1) Este regulamento tem como objetivo estabelecer a orienta\\u00e7\\u00f5es para a condu\\u00e7\\u00e3o do campeonato amador de kart de 2023 SPEEDKART.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;1.2) A comiss\\u00e3o se resguarda no direito de reavaliar, alterar ou complementar as regras, uma vez, at\\u00e9 a sexta etapa da temporada, caso as demandas sejam necess\\u00e1rias.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;1.3) O esp\\u00edrito do campeonato \\u00e9 incentivar a competitividade sadia e a participa\\u00e7\\u00e3o em equipe. Nossa meta \\u00e9 ter todos os pilotos participando de disputas limpas, mantendo a rivalidade sem perder a amizade.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2023-02-08 17:11:58\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-02-09 18:11:21\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2023-02-09 18:10:36\",\"publish_up\":\"2023-02-08 17:11:58\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":3,\"ordering\":\"2\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"67\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0),
(124, 20, 1, '', '2023-02-09 18:12:56', 676, 5815, '12a04c2635d23d5c350721a38d95b53ca1418bbe', '{\"id\":20,\"asset_id\":\"100\",\"title\":\"CAMPEONATO\",\"alias\":\"inscricao\",\"introtext\":\"<p>O campeonato ser\\u00e1 dividido em duas categorias, FAST e FURIOUS,sendo disputado em at\\u00e9 12 etapas (podendo haver altera\\u00e7\\u00f5es por motivo de for\\u00e7a maior).<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>A comiss\\u00e3o organizadora avaliar\\u00e1 o n\\u00edvel t\\u00e9cnico e desempenho dos pilotos e ir\\u00e1 direcion\\u00e1los para uma das duas categorias FAST ou FURIOUS.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>As etapas de junho para a categoria FAST e agosto para a categoria FURIOUS, ser\\u00e3o etapas com corridas de 50 minutos (endurance), com uma volta obrigat\\u00f3ria de pelo menos 4 minutos e troca obrigat\\u00f3ria de kart durante a corrida.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>N\\u00e3o haver\\u00e1 pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o diferente nestas etapas.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Para a classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o de pilotos das categorias FAST e FURIOUS, ser\\u00e3o desconsiderados\\/descartados os dois piores resultado de cada piloto (um na primeira etapa, de janeiro a junho e outra na segunda etapa, julho a dezembro), incluindo sua aus\\u00eancia em alguma das etapas;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Para a classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o geral por equipes, ser\\u00e1 descartada, em cada uma das doze etapas, a pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o do piloto com o pior resultado de posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o da corrida, ou a pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o zerada do piloto que se ausentar nas etapas, somando para a classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o apenas a pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o dos melhores pilotos da equipe naquela etapa. Caso haja mais de um piloto da equipe ausente na mesma corrida, apenas, uma pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o zerada poder\\u00e1 ser considerada descarte. Os demais ausentes ter\\u00e3o sua pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o, ainda que tamb\\u00e9m zerada, inclusa na somat\\u00f3ria dos pontos da respectiva etapa.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Para a classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o geral por equipes, N\\u00c3O ser\\u00e3o desconsiderados\\/descartados o pior resultado de cada piloto como na classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o de pilotos.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Haver\\u00e1 premia\\u00e7\\u00e3o do primeiro ao quinto lugar em todas as etapas, sendo considerado campe\\u00e3o da temporada aquele piloto que alcan\\u00e7ar a maior pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o nas etapas de janeiro a dezembro.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>O campeonato ter\\u00e1 uma premia\\u00e7\\u00e3o extra para o piloto de cada categoria que alcan\\u00e7ar a maior pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o nas etapas de janeiro a junho e ser\\u00e1 considerado o campe\\u00e3o do primeiro semestre, o mesmo ocorrer\\u00e1 com o piloto de cada categoria que tiver a maior pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o de julho a dezembro sendo considerado o campe\\u00e3o do segundo semestre.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Para a defini\\u00e7\\u00e3o do campe\\u00e3o do segundo semestre, a pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o ser\\u00e1 zerada no final do primeiro semestre (janeiro a junho).&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Para pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o destas etapas ser\\u00e3o consideradas a mesma pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o e penalidades previstas no campeonato.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Nenhuma etapa poder\\u00e1 ser adiada, anulada ou antecipada, a n\\u00e3o ser com aceite m\\u00ednimo de dois ter\\u00e7os dos participantes ou por motivo de for\\u00e7a maior;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>A classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o das equipes ser\\u00e1 \\u00fanica e a pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o ser\\u00e1 baseada na classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o do piloto em sua categoria.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Ap\\u00f3s cada corrida, OS PILOTOS que chegarem entre a 1\\u00aa e a 5\\u00aa coloca\\u00e7\\u00e3o dever\\u00e3o subir na balan\\u00e7a e realizar a pesagem. O peso oficial do campeonato para as categorias FAST \\u00e9 de 100kg e para a categoria FURIOUS \\u00e9 de 110kg. Caso o conjunto piloto, capacete, macac\\u00e3o e demais acess\\u00f3rios ficar abaixo desse peso, o piloto ser\\u00e1 desclassificado da corrida, ficando os pr\\u00f3ximos classificados na etapa a pesarem da mesma forma.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Haver\\u00e1 uma toler\\u00e2ncia de no m\\u00e1ximo 500g da pesagem do piloto com rela\\u00e7\\u00e3o ao limite m\\u00ednimo de peso da categoria.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>O piloto \\u00e9 respons\\u00e1vel por colocar o lastro no Kart. Caso o piloto seja flagrado descumprindo o disposto nos itens 3.5 e 3.5.1 deste regulamento, o mesmo ser\\u00e1 punido com a desclassifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o da corrida.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-02-09 18:12:56\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2023-02-09 18:12:28\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":13,\"ordering\":\"10\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"335\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0),
(125, 94, 1, '', '2023-02-09 18:26:08', 676, 5391, '93c655ef3737d2f395f454c3edb870b4df2ece72', '{\"id\":94,\"asset_id\":\"447\",\"title\":\"PARTICIPA\\u00c7\\u00c3O\",\"alias\":\"participacao\",\"introtext\":\"<p>2.1) Os pilotos da categoria FAST e FURIUS ser\\u00e3o divididos em equipes com no m\\u00ednimo tr\\u00eas pilotos, que ser\\u00e3o divididas pela comiss\\u00e3o organizadora antes do in\\u00edcio do campeonato. As equipes disputar\\u00e3o o t\\u00edtulo apenas contra equipes da mesma categoria. Ser\\u00e1 respeitado a divis\\u00e3o de pilotos conforme a categoria, o desempenho e a qualidade de cada piloto, mantendo as equipes o mais equilibradas poss\\u00edvel.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp; 2.1.1) Nenhum piloto poder\\u00e1 trocar de equipe ou de categoria durante a temporada a n\\u00e3o ser para compor uma nova equipe, ficando a crit\\u00e9rio da comiss\\u00e3o essa decis\\u00e3o.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>2.2) Com o objetivo de prestigiar e divulgar a marca dos patrocinadores do campeonato, ser\\u00e1 obrigat\\u00f3rio o uso da camisa oficial do campeonato SPEEDKART 2023 para chegar ao kart\\u00f3dromo. O piloto que n\\u00e3o comparecer ao kart\\u00f3dromo usando a camisa, perder\\u00e1 5 pontos. Esta regra entra em vigor ap\\u00f3s entrega das camisas.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp; 2.2.1) Os pilotos inscritos receber\\u00e3o uma camisa personalizada e um bon\\u00e9 do campeonato.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>2.3)&nbsp;Durante a corrida \\u00e9 obrigat\\u00f3ria a identifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o do piloto, podendo ser feita pelo uso da camisa com o nome por cima do macac\\u00e3o, nome gravado na parte traseira ou lateral do capacete ou com o nome nas costas ou na perna do macac\\u00e3o. (o nome tem que ser de tamanho vis\\u00edvel e dever\\u00e1 ser aprovada pela comiss\\u00e3o) cujo objetivo \\u00e9 identificar o piloto durante a prova. O uso de equipamentos que impe\\u00e7am a identifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o do piloto, n\\u00e3o \\u00e9 permitido.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>2.4)&nbsp;Ao confirmar a inscri\\u00e7\\u00e3o no campeonato, o piloto fica ciente e assume o compromisso do pagamento das taxas de inscri\\u00e7\\u00e3o e de participar de toda a temporada.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\">&nbsp; 2.4.1)&nbsp;Em caso de desist\\u00eancia e sa\\u00edda do campeonato, o piloto poder\\u00e1 indicar outro para assumir o seu lugar. A comiss\\u00e3o avaliar\\u00e1 a entrada desse novo piloto, podendo vetar a participa\\u00e7\\u00e3o deste.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\">&nbsp; 2.4.2)&nbsp;Caso o piloto seja aprovado pela comiss\\u00e3o, ele assumir\\u00e1 os pontos e puni\\u00e7\\u00f5es do piloto substitu\\u00eddo.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\">&nbsp; 2.4.3)&nbsp;Caso o piloto n\\u00e3o indique outro para seu lugar, a comiss\\u00e3o reserva o direito de n\\u00e3o devolver o valor da inscri\\u00e7\\u00e3o pago,&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ficando o piloto obrigado a pagar at\\u00e9 o m\\u00eas da desist\\u00eancia.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>2.5)&nbsp;Ser\\u00e1 permitido pilotos convidados que queiram conhecer o campeonato, respeitando as formas descritas abaixo:&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp; 2.5.1)&nbsp;O piloto convidado sempre largar\\u00e1 na \\u00faltima posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o do grid.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp; 2.5.2)&nbsp;O piloto convidado poder\\u00e1 participar de uma categoria definida pela comiss\\u00e3o.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp; 2.5.3)&nbsp;N\\u00e3o ser\\u00e1 permitido a participa\\u00e7\\u00e3o de convidados a partir da nona etapa.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>2.6)&nbsp;Os karts a serem utilizados no campeonato das categorias FAST e FURIOUS ser\\u00e3o o SUPERKART, podendo, por\\u00e9m, em casos fortuitos ou de for\\u00e7a maior, ser utilizado o kart indoor.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>2.7)&nbsp;Para garantir a frequ\\u00eancia dos pilotos nas corridas at\\u00e9 o final do campeonato, aqueles pilotos que tiverem participado das 11 primeiras etapas do campeonato, n\\u00e3o pagar\\u00e1 a corrida da etapa de dezembro.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2023-02-08 17:31:46\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-02-09 18:26:08\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2023-02-09 18:20:47\",\"publish_up\":\"2023-02-08 17:31:46\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":4,\"ordering\":\"1\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"30\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\