(129, 94, 1, '', '2023-02-09 18:30:22', 676, 5669, '0ece643aa9a3dc89b7ffab69e614f979ad1943e5', '{\"id\":94,\"asset_id\":\"447\",\"title\":\"PARTICIPA\\u00c7\\u00c3O\",\"alias\":\"participacao\",\"introtext\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\">2.1) Os pilotos da categoria FAST e FURIUS ser\\u00e3o divididos em equipes com no m\\u00ednimo tr\\u00eas pilotos, que ser\\u00e3o divididas pela comiss\\u00e3o organizadora antes do in\\u00edcio do campeonato. As equipes disputar\\u00e3o o t\\u00edtulo apenas contra equipes da mesma categoria. Ser\\u00e1 respeitado a divis\\u00e3o de pilotos conforme a categoria, o desempenho e a qualidade de cada piloto, mantendo as equipes o mais equilibradas poss\\u00edvel.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\">2.1.1) Nenhum piloto poder\\u00e1 trocar de equipe ou de categoria durante a temporada a n\\u00e3o ser para compor uma nova equipe, ficando&nbsp; a crit\\u00e9rio da comiss\\u00e3o essa decis\\u00e3o.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\">2.2) Com o objetivo de prestigiar e divulgar a marca dos patrocinadores do campeonato, ser\\u00e1 obrigat\\u00f3rio o uso da camisa oficial do campeonato SPEEDKART 2023 para chegar ao kart\\u00f3dromo. O piloto que n\\u00e3o comparecer ao kart\\u00f3dromo usando a camisa, perder\\u00e1 5 pontos. Esta regra entra em vigor ap\\u00f3s entrega das camisas.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\">2.2.1) Os pilotos inscritos receber\\u00e3o uma camisa personalizada e um bon\\u00e9 do campeonato.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\">2.3)&nbsp;Durante a corrida \\u00e9 obrigat\\u00f3ria a identifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o do piloto, podendo ser feita pelo uso da camisa com o nome por cima do macac\\u00e3o, nome gravado na parte traseira ou lateral do capacete ou com o nome nas costas ou na perna do macac\\u00e3o. (o nome tem que ser de tamanho vis\\u00edvel e dever\\u00e1 ser aprovada pela comiss\\u00e3o) cujo objetivo \\u00e9 identificar o piloto durante a prova. O uso de equipamentos que impe\\u00e7am a identifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o do piloto, n\\u00e3o \\u00e9 permitido.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\">2.4)&nbsp;Ao confirmar a inscri\\u00e7\\u00e3o no campeonato, o piloto fica ciente e assume o compromisso do pagamento das taxas de inscri\\u00e7\\u00e3o e de participar de toda a temporada.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\">2.4.1)&nbsp;Em caso de desist\\u00eancia e sa\\u00edda do campeonato, o piloto poder\\u00e1 indicar outro para assumir o seu lugar. A comiss\\u00e3o avaliar\\u00e1 a&nbsp; entrada desse novo piloto, podendo vetar a participa\\u00e7\\u00e3o deste.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\">2.4.2)&nbsp;Caso o piloto seja aprovado pela comiss\\u00e3o, ele assumir\\u00e1 os pontos e puni\\u00e7\\u00f5es do piloto substitu\\u00eddo.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\">2.4.3)&nbsp;Caso o piloto n\\u00e3o indique outro para seu lugar, a comiss\\u00e3o reserva o direito de n\\u00e3o devolver o valor da inscri\\u00e7\\u00e3o pago,&nbsp; &nbsp; ficando o piloto obrigado a pagar at\\u00e9 o m\\u00eas da desist\\u00eancia.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\">2.5)&nbsp;Ser\\u00e1 permitido pilotos convidados que queiram conhecer o campeonato, respeitando as formas descritas abaixo:&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\">2.5.1)&nbsp;O piloto convidado sempre largar\\u00e1 na \\u00faltima posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o do grid.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\">2.5.2)&nbsp;O piloto convidado poder\\u00e1 participar de uma categoria definida pela comiss\\u00e3o.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\">2.5.3)&nbsp;N\\u00e3o ser\\u00e1 permitido a participa\\u00e7\\u00e3o de convidados a partir da nona etapa.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\">2.6)&nbsp;Os karts a serem utilizados no campeonato das categorias FAST e FURIOUS ser\\u00e3o o SUPERKART, podendo, por\\u00e9m, em casos fortuitos ou de for\\u00e7a maior, ser utilizado o kart indoor.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\">2.7)&nbsp;Para garantir a frequ\\u00eancia dos pilotos nas corridas at\\u00e9 o final do campeonato, aqueles pilotos que tiverem participado das 11 primeiras etapas do campeonato, n\\u00e3o pagar\\u00e1 a corrida da etapa de dezembro.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2023-02-08 17:31:46\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-02-09 18:30:22\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2023-02-09 18:29:56\",\"publish_up\":\"2023-02-08 17:31:46\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":8,\"ordering\":\"1\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"34\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0),
(130, 20, 1, '', '2023-02-09 18:36:03', 676, 5922, 'bf54d65d0ce79422144fa0b8e1d5239820e85e8f', '{\"id\":20,\"asset_id\":\"100\",\"title\":\"3. CAMPEONATO\",\"alias\":\"inscricao\",\"introtext\":\"<p>3.1) O campeonato ser\\u00e1 dividido em duas categorias, FAST e FURIOUS,sendo disputado em at\\u00e9 12 etapas (podendo haver altera\\u00e7\\u00f5es por motivo de for\\u00e7a maior).<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.1.1) A comiss\\u00e3o organizadora avaliar\\u00e1 o n\\u00edvel t\\u00e9cnico e desempenho dos pilotos e ir\\u00e1 direcion\\u00e1los para uma das duas categorias FAST ou FURIOUS.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.1.2) As etapas de junho para a categoria FAST e agosto para a categoria FURIOUS, ser\\u00e3o etapas com corridas de 50 minutos (endurance), com uma volta obrigat\\u00f3ria de pelo menos 4 minutos e troca obrigat\\u00f3ria de kart durante a corrida.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.1.2.1) N\\u00e3o haver\\u00e1 pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o diferente nestas etapas.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.2) Para a classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o de pilotos das categorias FAST e FURIOUS, ser\\u00e3o desconsiderados\\/descartados os dois piores resultado de cada piloto (um na primeira etapa, de janeiro a junho e outra na segunda etapa, julho a dezembro), incluindo sua aus\\u00eancia em alguma das etapas;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.2.1) Para a classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o geral por equipes, ser\\u00e1 descartada, em cada uma das doze etapas, a pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o do piloto com o pior resultado de posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o da corrida, ou a pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o zerada do piloto que se ausentar nas etapas, somando para a classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o apenas a pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o dos melhores pilotos da equipe naquela etapa. Caso haja mais de um piloto da equipe ausente na mesma corrida, apenas, uma pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o zerada poder\\u00e1 ser considerada descarte. Os demais ausentes ter\\u00e3o sua pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o, ainda que tamb\\u00e9m zerada, inclusa na somat\\u00f3ria dos pontos da respectiva etapa.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.2.2) Para a classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o geral por equipes, N\\u00c3O ser\\u00e3o desconsiderados\\/descartados o pior resultado de cada piloto como na classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o de pilotos.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.2.3) Haver\\u00e1 premia\\u00e7\\u00e3o do primeiro ao quinto lugar em todas as etapas, sendo considerado campe\\u00e3o da temporada aquele piloto que alcan\\u00e7ar a maior pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o nas etapas de janeiro a dezembro.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.2.4) O campeonato ter\\u00e1 uma premia\\u00e7\\u00e3o extra para o piloto de cada categoria que alcan\\u00e7ar a maior pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o nas etapas de janeiro a junho e ser\\u00e1 considerado o campe\\u00e3o do primeiro semestre, o mesmo ocorrer\\u00e1 com o piloto de cada categoria que tiver a maior pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o de julho a dezembro sendo considerado o campe\\u00e3o do segundo semestre.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.2.5) Para a defini\\u00e7\\u00e3o do campe\\u00e3o do segundo semestre, a pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o ser\\u00e1 zerada no final do primeiro semestre (janeiro a junho).&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.2.6) Para pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o destas etapas ser\\u00e3o consideradas a mesma pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o e penalidades previstas no campeonato.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.3) Nenhuma etapa poder\\u00e1 ser adiada, anulada ou antecipada, a n\\u00e3o ser com aceite m\\u00ednimo de dois ter\\u00e7os dos participantes ou por motivo de for\\u00e7a maior;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.4) A classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o das equipes ser\\u00e1 \\u00fanica e a pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o ser\\u00e1 baseada na classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o do piloto em sua categoria.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.5) Ap\\u00f3s cada corrida, OS PILOTOS que chegarem entre a 1\\u00aa e a 5\\u00aa coloca\\u00e7\\u00e3o dever\\u00e3o subir na balan\\u00e7a e realizar a pesagem. O peso oficial do campeonato para as categorias FAST \\u00e9 de 100kg e para a categoria FURIOUS \\u00e9 de 110kg. Caso o conjunto piloto, capacete, macac\\u00e3o e demais acess\\u00f3rios ficar abaixo desse peso, o piloto ser\\u00e1 desclassificado da corrida, ficando os pr\\u00f3ximos classificados na etapa a pesarem da mesma forma.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.5.1) Haver\\u00e1 uma toler\\u00e2ncia de no m\\u00e1ximo 500g da pesagem do piloto com rela\\u00e7\\u00e3o ao limite m\\u00ednimo de peso da categoria.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.5.2) O piloto \\u00e9 respons\\u00e1vel por colocar o lastro no Kart. Caso o piloto seja flagrado descumprindo o disposto nos itens 3.5 e 3.5.1 deste regulamento, o mesmo ser\\u00e1 punido com a desclassifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o da corrida.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-02-09 18:36:03\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2023-02-09 18:31:15\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":14,\"ordering\":\"10\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"340\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0),
(131, 20, 1, '', '2023-02-09 18:36:22', 676, 5919, '0432aae2c865d4b77ee580e78754f5a19fdbe933', '{\"id\":20,\"asset_id\":\"100\",\"title\":\"CAMPEONATO\",\"alias\":\"inscricao\",\"introtext\":\"<p>3.1) O campeonato ser\\u00e1 dividido em duas categorias, FAST e FURIOUS,sendo disputado em at\\u00e9 12 etapas (podendo haver altera\\u00e7\\u00f5es por motivo de for\\u00e7a maior).<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.1.1) A comiss\\u00e3o organizadora avaliar\\u00e1 o n\\u00edvel t\\u00e9cnico e desempenho dos pilotos e ir\\u00e1 direcion\\u00e1los para uma das duas categorias FAST ou FURIOUS.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.1.2) As etapas de junho para a categoria FAST e agosto para a categoria FURIOUS, ser\\u00e3o etapas com corridas de 50 minutos (endurance), com uma volta obrigat\\u00f3ria de pelo menos 4 minutos e troca obrigat\\u00f3ria de kart durante a corrida.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.1.2.1) N\\u00e3o haver\\u00e1 pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o diferente nestas etapas.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.2) Para a classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o de pilotos das categorias FAST e FURIOUS, ser\\u00e3o desconsiderados\\/descartados os dois piores resultado de cada piloto (um na primeira etapa, de janeiro a junho e outra na segunda etapa, julho a dezembro), incluindo sua aus\\u00eancia em alguma das etapas;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.2.1) Para a classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o geral por equipes, ser\\u00e1 descartada, em cada uma das doze etapas, a pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o do piloto com o pior resultado de posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o da corrida, ou a pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o zerada do piloto que se ausentar nas etapas, somando para a classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o apenas a pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o dos melhores pilotos da equipe naquela etapa. Caso haja mais de um piloto da equipe ausente na mesma corrida, apenas, uma pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o zerada poder\\u00e1 ser considerada descarte. Os demais ausentes ter\\u00e3o sua pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o, ainda que tamb\\u00e9m zerada, inclusa na somat\\u00f3ria dos pontos da respectiva etapa.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.2.2) Para a classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o geral por equipes, N\\u00c3O ser\\u00e3o desconsiderados\\/descartados o pior resultado de cada piloto como na classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o de pilotos.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.2.3) Haver\\u00e1 premia\\u00e7\\u00e3o do primeiro ao quinto lugar em todas as etapas, sendo considerado campe\\u00e3o da temporada aquele piloto que alcan\\u00e7ar a maior pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o nas etapas de janeiro a dezembro.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.2.4) O campeonato ter\\u00e1 uma premia\\u00e7\\u00e3o extra para o piloto de cada categoria que alcan\\u00e7ar a maior pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o nas etapas de janeiro a junho e ser\\u00e1 considerado o campe\\u00e3o do primeiro semestre, o mesmo ocorrer\\u00e1 com o piloto de cada categoria que tiver a maior pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o de julho a dezembro sendo considerado o campe\\u00e3o do segundo semestre.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.2.5) Para a defini\\u00e7\\u00e3o do campe\\u00e3o do segundo semestre, a pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o ser\\u00e1 zerada no final do primeiro semestre (janeiro a junho).&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.2.6) Para pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o destas etapas ser\\u00e3o consideradas a mesma pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o e penalidades previstas no campeonato.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.3) Nenhuma etapa poder\\u00e1 ser adiada, anulada ou antecipada, a n\\u00e3o ser com aceite m\\u00ednimo de dois ter\\u00e7os dos participantes ou por motivo de for\\u00e7a maior;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.4) A classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o das equipes ser\\u00e1 \\u00fanica e a pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o ser\\u00e1 baseada na classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o do piloto em sua categoria.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.5) Ap\\u00f3s cada corrida, OS PILOTOS que chegarem entre a 1\\u00aa e a 5\\u00aa coloca\\u00e7\\u00e3o dever\\u00e3o subir na balan\\u00e7a e realizar a pesagem. O peso oficial do campeonato para as categorias FAST \\u00e9 de 100kg e para a categoria FURIOUS \\u00e9 de 110kg. Caso o conjunto piloto, capacete, macac\\u00e3o e demais acess\\u00f3rios ficar abaixo desse peso, o piloto ser\\u00e1 desclassificado da corrida, ficando os pr\\u00f3ximos classificados na etapa a pesarem da mesma forma.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.5.1) Haver\\u00e1 uma toler\\u00e2ncia de no m\\u00e1ximo 500g da pesagem do piloto com rela\\u00e7\\u00e3o ao limite m\\u00ednimo de peso da categoria.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>3.5.2) O piloto \\u00e9 respons\\u00e1vel por colocar o lastro no Kart. Caso o piloto seja flagrado descumprindo o disposto nos itens 3.5 e 3.5.1 deste regulamento, o mesmo ser\\u00e1 punido com a desclassifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o da corrida.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-02-09 18:36:22\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2023-02-09 18:36:03\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":15,\"ordering\":\"10\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"341\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0),
(132, 26, 1, '', '2023-02-09 18:41:42', 676, 2422, '26a851710fca03381e48ebb972be7bd09beacf73', '{\"id\":26,\"asset_id\":\"106\",\"title\":\"PONTUA\\u00c7\\u00c3O\",\"alias\":\"comissao\",\"introtext\":\"<p>4.1) A pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o de pilotos ser\\u00e1 realizada de acordo com a tabela abaixo:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\\"images\\/PONTUA\\u00c7\\u00c3O1.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>4.2) A pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o por equipes ser\\u00e1 realizada de acordo com a tabela abaixo respeitando o resultado do piloto em sua categoria:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><img src=\\\"images\\/PONTUA\\u00c7\\u00c3O1.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #ff0000;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #ffffff;\\\">4.3)<\\/span> Pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o b\\u00f4nus de melhor volta<\\/span>: Um piloto de cada categoria receber\\u00e1 1 (um) ponto por realizarem a melhor volta de sua categoria na corrida.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-02-09 18:41:42\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2023-02-09 18:40:45\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":6,\"ordering\":\"4\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"257\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0),
(133, 19, 1, '', '2023-02-09 18:45:20', 676, 3780, '931b49f2a295772a70d22a2e5e83ce17b3628b4c', '{\"id\":19,\"asset_id\":\"99\",\"title\":\"PREMIA\\u00c7\\u00c3O DO CAMPEONATO\",\"alias\":\"premiacao-do-campeonato\",\"introtext\":\"<p>5.1) A festa de confraterniza\\u00e7\\u00e3o, est\\u00e1 prevista para ser realizada em<strong><span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"> 03 de dezembro 2023<\\/span><\\/strong>, ap\\u00f3s a \\u00faltima corrida do ano, conforme as vezes passadas. Esta, por sua vez, ser\\u00e1 confirmada antes da \\u00faltima corrida, onde ser\\u00e3o entregues os trof\\u00e9us de pilotos, equipes e de participa\\u00e7\\u00e3o sendo:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;5.1.1)&nbsp; 01 (um) trof\\u00e9u para os 05 (cinco) melhores pilotos da categoria FAST.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;5.1.2) 01 (um) trof\\u00e9u para os 05 (cinco) melhores pilotos da categoria FURIOUS.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;5.1.3) 01 (um) trof\\u00e9u para cada piloto das 03 (tr\\u00eas) melhores equipes de cada categoria.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;5.1.4) 01 (um) trof\\u00e9u para o campe\\u00e3o do primeiro e segundo semestre.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>5.2) Crit\\u00e9rios de desempate na Classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o por pilotos:&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;5.2.1)&nbsp; 1\\u00b0 - Maior n\\u00famero de vit\\u00f3rias do piloto no campeonato;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;5.2.2) 2\\u00b0 - Maior n\\u00famero de 2\\u00aa posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o do piloto no campeonato;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;5.2.3) 3\\u00b0 - Maior n\\u00famero de 3\\u00aa posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o do piloto no campeonato, e assim sucessivamente.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>5.3) Crit\\u00e9rios de desempate na Classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o das equipes:&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;5.3.1)&nbsp; 1\\u00b0 - Maior n\\u00famero de vit\\u00f3rias de pilotos da equipe no campeonato;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;5.3.2) 2\\u00b0 - Maior n\\u00famero de 2\\u00aa posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o de pilotos da equipe no campeonato;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;5.3.3) 3\\u00b0-Maior n\\u00famero de 3\\u00aa posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o de pilotos da equipe no campeonato, e assim sucessivamente.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>5.4) Os trof\\u00e9us da Categoria FAST e FURIOUS a serem entregues nas etapas constar\\u00e3o a categoria e a Coloca\\u00e7\\u00e3o do piloto: Campe\\u00e3o, Vice-campe\\u00e3o, Terceiro, Quarto e Quinto lugares.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-02-09 18:45:20\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2023-02-09 18:41:52\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":6,\"ordering\":\"11\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"359\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0);
