(142, 19, 1, '', '2023-02-09 21:39:19', 676, 4020, 'f66d263c53de360db9867605722237bd9116be97', '{\"id\":19,\"asset_id\":\"99\",\"title\":\"PREMIA\\u00c7\\u00c3O DO CAMPEONATO\",\"alias\":\"premiacao-do-campeonato\",\"introtext\":\"<p>5.1) A festa de confraterniza\\u00e7\\u00e3o, est\\u00e1 prevista para ser realizada em<strong><span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"> 03 de dezembro 2023<\\/span><\\/strong>, ap\\u00f3s a \\u00faltima corrida do ano, conforme as vezes passadas. Esta, por sua vez, ser\\u00e1 confirmada antes da \\u00faltima corrida, onde ser\\u00e3o entregues os trof\\u00e9us de pilotos, equipes e de participa\\u00e7\\u00e3o sendo:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.1.1)&nbsp; 01 (um) trof\\u00e9u para os 05 (cinco) melhores pilotos da categoria FAST.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.1.2) 01 (um) trof\\u00e9u para os 05 (cinco) melhores pilotos da categoria FURIOUS.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.1.3) 01 (um) trof\\u00e9u para cada piloto das 03 (tr\\u00eas) melhores equipes de cada categoria.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.1.4) 01 (um) trof\\u00e9u para o campe\\u00e3o do primeiro e segundo semestre.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>5.2) Crit\\u00e9rios de desempate na Classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o por pilotos:&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.2.1)&nbsp; 1\\u00b0 - Maior n\\u00famero de vit\\u00f3rias do piloto no campeonato;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.2.2) 2\\u00b0 - Maior n\\u00famero de 2\\u00aa posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o do piloto no campeonato;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.2.3) 3\\u00b0 - Maior n\\u00famero de 3\\u00aa posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o do piloto no campeonato, e assim sucessivamente.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>5.3) Crit\\u00e9rios de desempate na Classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o das equipes:&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.3.1)&nbsp; 1\\u00b0 - Maior n\\u00famero de vit\\u00f3rias de pilotos da equipe no campeonato;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.3.2) 2\\u00b0 - Maior n\\u00famero de 2\\u00aa posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o de pilotos da equipe no campeonato;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.3.3) 3\\u00b0-Maior n\\u00famero de 3\\u00aa posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o de pilotos da equipe no campeonato, e assim sucessivamente.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>5.4) Os trof\\u00e9us da Categoria FAST e FURIOUS a serem entregues nas etapas constar\\u00e3o a categoria e a Coloca\\u00e7\\u00e3o do piloto: Campe\\u00e3o, Vice-campe\\u00e3o, Terceiro, Quarto e Quinto lugares.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-02-09 21:39:19\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2023-02-09 21:38:22\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":8,\"ordering\":\"11\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"364\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0),
(143, 19, 1, '', '2023-02-09 21:39:57', 676, 4023, 'c0862acc832c4aba8ab0bb6184ed58aee43f3d43', '{\"id\":19,\"asset_id\":\"99\",\"title\":\"5. PREMIA\\u00c7\\u00c3O DO CAMPEONATO\",\"alias\":\"premiacao-do-campeonato\",\"introtext\":\"<p>5.1) A festa de confraterniza\\u00e7\\u00e3o, est\\u00e1 prevista para ser realizada em<strong><span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"> 03 de dezembro 2023<\\/span><\\/strong>, ap\\u00f3s a \\u00faltima corrida do ano, conforme as vezes passadas. Esta, por sua vez, ser\\u00e1 confirmada antes da \\u00faltima corrida, onde ser\\u00e3o entregues os trof\\u00e9us de pilotos, equipes e de participa\\u00e7\\u00e3o sendo:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.1.1)&nbsp; 01 (um) trof\\u00e9u para os 05 (cinco) melhores pilotos da categoria FAST.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.1.2) 01 (um) trof\\u00e9u para os 05 (cinco) melhores pilotos da categoria FURIOUS.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.1.3) 01 (um) trof\\u00e9u para cada piloto das 03 (tr\\u00eas) melhores equipes de cada categoria.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.1.4) 01 (um) trof\\u00e9u para o campe\\u00e3o do primeiro e segundo semestre.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>5.2) Crit\\u00e9rios de desempate na Classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o por pilotos:&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.2.1)&nbsp; 1\\u00b0 - Maior n\\u00famero de vit\\u00f3rias do piloto no campeonato;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.2.2) 2\\u00b0 - Maior n\\u00famero de 2\\u00aa posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o do piloto no campeonato;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.2.3) 3\\u00b0 - Maior n\\u00famero de 3\\u00aa posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o do piloto no campeonato, e assim sucessivamente.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>5.3) Crit\\u00e9rios de desempate na Classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o das equipes:&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.3.1)&nbsp; 1\\u00b0 - Maior n\\u00famero de vit\\u00f3rias de pilotos da equipe no campeonato;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.3.2) 2\\u00b0 - Maior n\\u00famero de 2\\u00aa posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o de pilotos da equipe no campeonato;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.3.3) 3\\u00b0-Maior n\\u00famero de 3\\u00aa posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o de pilotos da equipe no campeonato, e assim sucessivamente.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>5.4) Os trof\\u00e9us da Categoria FAST e FURIOUS a serem entregues nas etapas constar\\u00e3o a categoria e a Coloca\\u00e7\\u00e3o do piloto: Campe\\u00e3o, Vice-campe\\u00e3o, Terceiro, Quarto e Quinto lugares.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-02-09 21:39:57\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2023-02-09 21:39:19\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":9,\"ordering\":\"11\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"364\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0),
(144, 15, 1, '', '2023-02-09 21:43:47', 676, 4558, '9e77fcd3fa6b09b0a03e356296582e3c93066224', '{\"id\":15,\"asset_id\":\"95\",\"title\":\"BRIEFING\",\"alias\":\"premiacao\",\"introtext\":\"<p>6.1) No dia da corrida os pilotos devem chegar ao kart\\u00f3dromo no m\\u00ednimo com 30 (trinta) minutos de anteced\\u00eancia ao hor\\u00e1rio previsto para o in\\u00edcio da corrida.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>6.2) Est\\u00e1 previsto o in\\u00edcio do briefing da corrida com 30 minutos antes da largada.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">6.2.1) O piloto deve estar inscrito na corrida at\\u00e9 o final da pesagem e sorteio dos KARTS. Quem chegar ap\\u00f3s o in\\u00edcio do briefing, mesmo que esteja nas depend\\u00eancias do kart\\u00f3dromo, ir\\u00e1 largar da \\u00faltima posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o de sua categoria. Caso mais de 1 piloto se atrasar, a posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o ser\\u00e1 pela ordem de chegada a partir da \\u00faltima posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o do grid.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>6.3) Os Karts ser\\u00e3o definidos por SORTEIO no briefing que antecede a corrida. O sorteio ser\\u00e1 realizado pelo diretor de prova juntamente com a equipe do kart\\u00f3dromo.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>6.4) O grid ser\\u00e1 montado na ordem inversa da posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o de classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o do campeonato, conforme a categoria. E poder\\u00e1 come\\u00e7ar tanto com os pilotos da categoria FAST, quanto com os pilotos da categoria FURIOUS.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">6.4.1) O grid das categorias Fast e Furious na primeira corrida (janeiro) ser\\u00e1 definido por tomada de tempo de cinco minutos.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">6.4.2) A largada ser\\u00e1 em movimento e em fila DUPLA.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">6.4.3) Durante as voltas de alinhamento e largada \\u00e9 proibido a ultrapassagem. A exce\\u00e7\\u00e3o \\u00e9: defeito, sa\\u00edda de pista, derrapagem ou indica\\u00e7\\u00e3o da organiza\\u00e7\\u00e3o do kart\\u00f3dromo.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">6.4.4) Durante a volta de alinhamento, o piloto deve manter sua posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o LADO A LADO com o piloto de refer\\u00eancia ao seu lado e, por conseguinte, manter dist\\u00e2ncia de seguran\\u00e7a com os pilotos a sua frente. Caso por alguma imper\\u00edcia o piloto vir a derrapar, rodar e\\/ou sair da pista com o kart, dever\\u00e1 aguardar o fim do pelot\\u00e3o de largada.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>6.5) N\\u00e3o ser\\u00e1 permitido ao piloto, em hip\\u00f3tese alguma, fazer qualquer tipo de regulagem, ou altera\\u00e7\\u00e3o no kart que o piloto receber no sorteio tanto com o kart parado quanto em movimento. A \\u00fanica regulagem autorizada \\u00e9 a da posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o de banco, qualquer outra, somente poder\\u00e1 ser efetuada pelos mec\\u00e2nicos da pista; Exceto se houver algum problema no kart.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>6.6) O piloto poder\\u00e1 substituir o seu kart, obrigatoriamente, por outro kart sorteado pelo kart\\u00f3dromo, e ir\\u00e1 largar na \\u00faltima posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o do grid.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-02-09 21:43:47\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2023-02-09 21:42:58\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":11,\"ordering\":\"15\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"345\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0),
(145, 21, 1, '', '2023-02-09 21:47:30', 676, 6132, '0d8e4ede741da6ff5b908117e79938d2aba2ae8f', '{\"id\":21,\"asset_id\":\"101\",\"title\":\"PUNI\\u00c7\\u00d5ES\",\"alias\":\"punicoes\",\"introtext\":\"<p>7.1) As puni\\u00e7\\u00f5es com perda de pontos ser\\u00e3o aplicadas no somat\\u00f3rio da pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o da classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o dos pilotos e equipes, e n\\u00e3o ser\\u00e3o retiradas em caso de o resultado da etapa ser usado na classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o como descarte.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>7.2) O piloto que n\\u00e3o se apresentar utilizando a camisa oficial do SPEEDKART, receber\\u00e1 a puni\\u00e7\\u00e3o de 5 pontos.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>7.3) Haver\\u00e1 uma puni\\u00e7\\u00e3o de 05 (cinco) pontos, em cada prova que o piloto correr sem a devida identifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o; para n\\u00e3o perder os pontos os pilotos dever\\u00e3o se identificar com nome VIS\\u00cdVEL no macac\\u00e3o, capacete ou com a camisa do SPEEDKART.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>7.4) O piloto que derrubar os cones colocados para sinalizar a passagem da largada ou instalados para sinaliza\\u00e7\\u00e3o na pista receber\\u00e1 uma puni\\u00e7\\u00e3o de 5 (cinco) pontos.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>7.5) O piloto que receber uma advert\\u00eancia do kart\\u00f3dromo por imprud\\u00eancia e\\/ou conduta antiesportiva, ser\\u00e1 penalizado em 5 (cinco) posi\\u00e7\\u00f5es no resultado da corrida, que ser\\u00e1 aplicada imediatamente ap\\u00f3s a realiza\\u00e7\\u00e3o da corrida, n\\u00e3o havendo possibilidade de recurso para esse tipo de penalidade.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>7.6) Para condutas antidesportivas que n\\u00e3o foram registradas pelo kart\\u00f3dromo, por\\u00e9m capturadas por c\\u00e2meras na bateria, esta ser\\u00e1 analisada pela comiss\\u00e3o disciplinar para defini\\u00e7\\u00e3o de poss\\u00edvel puni\\u00e7\\u00e3o. Para esse caso, o prazo m\\u00e1ximo ser\\u00e1 de at\\u00e9 05 (cinco) dias ap\\u00f3s a corrida. Caso confirmado, o piloto infrator receber\\u00e1 uma puni\\u00e7\\u00e3o de 5(cinco) posi\\u00e7\\u00f5es no resultado da corrida. Caso o piloto que causou a infra\\u00e7\\u00e3o tenha se beneficiado e subido ao p\\u00f3dio, esse, por sua vez, dever\\u00e1 devolver o trof\\u00e9u que ser\\u00e1 encaminhado a quem de direito.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>7.7) Caso algum piloto se sinta prejudicado na corrida por algum oponente este, por sua vez, dever\\u00e1 procurar a comiss\\u00e3o disciplinar e relatar o ocorrido, registrando a reclama\\u00e7\\u00e3o formalmente por escrito (via whatsapp ou e-mail). A comiss\\u00e3o ir\\u00e1 analisar a reclama\\u00e7\\u00e3o, consultando os envolvidos e os poss\\u00edveis testemunhos de outros pilotos. Caso confirmado, ser\\u00e1 aplicado a puni\\u00e7\\u00e3o de 05 (cinco) pontos ao piloto infrator.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">7.7.1) A reclama\\u00e7\\u00e3o deve ser enviada direto ao whatsapp da comiss\\u00e3o, n\\u00e3o deve ser postado no grupo do Speed kart 2023&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>7.8) O piloto que queimar a largada, realizar a ultrapassagem ou sair da linha antes da passagem pela linha de partida ser\\u00e1 punido com 05 (cinco) posi\\u00e7\\u00f5es no resultado da corrida.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>7.9) O piloto que for flagrado saindo com as 4 rodas para fora das faixas de delimita\\u00e7\\u00e3o da pista, para obter vantagem em ultrapassagens, ser\\u00e1 penalizado em 5 (cinco) posi\\u00e7\\u00f5es no resultado da corrida. Exceto quando o kart da frente estiver rodando ou danificado.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>7.10) N\\u00e3o \\u00e9 permitido ao piloto ficar mudando de faixa para impedir a ultrapassagem. \\u00c9 permitido o m\\u00e1ximo 2 mudan\\u00e7as de faixa, sendo a \\u00faltima se for necess\\u00e1rio para tomada de curva. O piloto flagrado nesta conduta ser\\u00e1 punido com 05 (cinco) posi\\u00e7\\u00f5es no resultado da corrida.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>7.11) Por ter o esp\\u00edrito amig\\u00e1vel e saud\\u00e1vel, n\\u00e3o ser\\u00e3o toleradas condutas agressivas ou ofensas verbais. Ser\\u00e1 aplicado um a puni\\u00e7\\u00e3o de 60 (sessenta) pontos para cada ocorr\\u00eancia. Em casos extremos, com concord\\u00e2ncia de maioria simples dos pilotos, os envolvidos ser\\u00e3o convidados a sa\\u00edrem do campeonato. Sem direito a qualquer ressarcimento.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>7.12) Nas etapas de endurance ser\\u00e3o aplicadas as regras do kartodormo,&nbsp;<span style=\\\"color: #ff0000;\\\"><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/rbcracing.com.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/11\\/REGULAMENTO-ENDURANCE-210KM.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" style=\\\"color: #ff0000;\\\">C<\\/a>lique aqui para visualizar as regras do kart\\u00f3dromo.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-02-09 21:47:30\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2023-02-09 21:46:13\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associat