(162, 26, 1, '', '2023-03-11 00:21:30', 676, 5091, 'f58cf391991e720b2a24ce6d1b25362a7750b031', '{\"id\":26,\"asset_id\":\"106\",\"title\":\"PONTUA\\u00c7\\u00c3O\",\"alias\":\"comissao\",\"introtext\":\"<p>4.1) A pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o de pilotos ser\\u00e1 realizada de acordo com a tabela abaixo:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>01\\u00ba &nbsp;- 30 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 09\\u00ba - 17 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 17\\u00ba - 9 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 25\\u00ba - 1 ponto<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>02\\u00ba &nbsp;- 27 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 10\\u00ba - 16 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 18\\u00ba - 8 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 26\\u00ba..... - 0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>03\\u00ba &nbsp;- 25 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 11\\u00ba - 15 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 19\\u00ba - 7 pontos&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>04\\u00ba &nbsp;- 23 pontos&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;12\\u00ba - 14 pontos&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 20\\u00ba - 6 pontos&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>05\\u00ba &nbsp;- 21 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 13\\u00ba - 13 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 21\\u00ba - 5 pontos&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>06\\u00ba &nbsp;- 20 pontos&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 14\\u00ba - 12 pontos&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 22\\u00ba - 4 pontos&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>07\\u00ba &nbsp;- 19 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 15\\u00ba - 11 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 23\\u00ba - 3 pontos&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>08\\u00ba &nbsp;- 18 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 16\\u00ba - 10 pontos&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 24\\u00ba - 2 pontos&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>4.2) A pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o por equipes ser\\u00e1 realizada de acordo com a tabela abaixo respeitando o resultado do piloto em sua categoria:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>01\\u00ba &nbsp;- 30 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 09\\u00ba - 17 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 17\\u00ba - 9 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 25\\u00ba - 1 ponto<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>02\\u00ba &nbsp;- 27 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 10\\u00ba - 16 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 18\\u00ba - 8 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 26\\u00ba..... - 0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>03\\u00ba &nbsp;- 25 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 11\\u00ba - 15 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 19\\u00ba - 7 pontos&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>04\\u00ba &nbsp;- 23 pontos&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;12\\u00ba - 14 pontos&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 20\\u00ba - 6 pontos&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>05\\u00ba &nbsp;- 21 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 13\\u00ba - 13 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 21\\u00ba - 5 pontos&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>06\\u00ba &nbsp;- 20 pontos&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 14\\u00ba - 12 pontos&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 22\\u00ba - 4 pontos&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>07\\u00ba &nbsp;- 19 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 15\\u00ba - 11 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 23\\u00ba - 3 pontos&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>08\\u00ba &nbsp;- 18 pontos &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 16\\u00ba - 10 pontos&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 24\\u00ba - 2 pontos&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"color: #ff0000;\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #ffffff;\\\">4.3)<\\/span> Pontua\\u00e7\\u00e3o b\\u00f4nus de melhor volta<\\/span>: Um piloto de cada categoria receber\\u00e1 1 (um) ponto por realizarem a melhor volta de sua categoria na corrida.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-03-11 00:21:30\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2023-03-11 00:19:16\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"i