(180, 19, 1, '', '2023-12-20 16:12:00', 676, 4018, 'c9dd0ab0d76f45ba9cc75f8cc48bdfc2b3246015', '{\"id\":19,\"asset_id\":\"99\",\"title\":\"5. PREMIA\\u00c7\\u00c3O DO CAMPEONATO\",\"alias\":\"premiacao-do-campeonato\",\"introtext\":\"<p>5.1) A festa de confraterniza\\u00e7\\u00e3o, est\\u00e1 prevista para ser realizada em<strong><span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"> dezembro 2024<\\/span><\\/strong>, ap\\u00f3s a \\u00faltima corrida do ano, conforme as vezes passadas. Esta, por sua vez, ser\\u00e1 confirmada antes da \\u00faltima corrida, onde ser\\u00e3o entregues os trof\\u00e9us de pilotos, equipes e de participa\\u00e7\\u00e3o sendo:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.1.1)&nbsp; 01 (um) trof\\u00e9u para os 05 (cinco) melhores pilotos da categoria FAST.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.1.2) 01 (um) trof\\u00e9u para os 05 (cinco) melhores pilotos da categoria FURIOUS.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.1.3) 01 (um) trof\\u00e9u para cada piloto das 03 (tr\\u00eas) melhores equipes de cada categoria.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.1.4) 01 (um) trof\\u00e9u para o campe\\u00e3o do primeiro e segundo semestre.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>5.2) Crit\\u00e9rios de desempate na Classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o por pilotos:&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.2.1)&nbsp; 1\\u00b0 - Maior n\\u00famero de vit\\u00f3rias do piloto no campeonato;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.2.2) 2\\u00b0 - Maior n\\u00famero de 2\\u00aa posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o do piloto no campeonato;&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.2.3) 3\\u00b0 - Maior n\\u00famero de 3\\u00aa posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o do piloto no campeonato, e assim sucessivamente.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>5.3) Crit\\u00e9rios de desempate na Classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o das equipes:&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.3.1)&nbsp; 1\\u00b0 - Maior n\\u00famero de vit\\u00f3rias de pilotos da equipe no campeonato;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.3.2) 2\\u00b0 - Maior n\\u00famero de 2\\u00aa posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o de pilotos da equipe no campeonato;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">5.3.3) 3\\u00b0-Maior n\\u00famero de 3\\u00aa posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o de pilotos da equipe no campeonato, e assim sucessivamente.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>5.4) Os trof\\u00e9us da Categoria FAST e FURIOUS a serem entregues nas etapas constar\\u00e3o a categoria e a Coloca\\u00e7\\u00e3o do piloto: Campe\\u00e3o, Vice-campe\\u00e3o, Terceiro, Quarto e Quinto lugares.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2023-12-20 16:12:00\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2023-12-20 16:10:59\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\