(186, 94, 1, '', '2024-01-30 14:08:59', 676, 3488, '00d140ef7f11ffcc120421c28993c22c67b73e85', '{\"id\":94,\"asset_id\":\"447\",\"title\":\"PARTICIPA\\u00c7\\u00c3O\",\"alias\":\"participacao\",\"introtext\":\"<p>2.1) Com o objetivo de prestigiar e divulgar a marca dos patrocinadores do campeonato, ser\\u00e1 obrigat\\u00f3rio o uso da camisa oficial do campeonato SPEEDKART 2024 para chegar ao kart\\u00f3dromo. O piloto que n\\u00e3o comparecer ao kart\\u00f3dromo usando a camisa, perder\\u00e1 5 pontos. Esta regra entra em vigor ap\\u00f3s entrega das camisas.<br \\/>2.1.1) Os pilotos inscritos receber\\u00e3o uma camisa personalizada e um bon\\u00e9 do campeonato.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>2.3) Ao confirmar a inscri\\u00e7\\u00e3o no campeonato, o piloto fica ciente e assume o compromisso do pagamento das taxas de inscri\\u00e7\\u00e3o e de participar de toda a temporada.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>2.3.1) Em caso de desist\\u00eancia e sa\\u00edda do campeonato, o piloto poder\\u00e1 indicar outro para assumir o seu lugar. A comiss\\u00e3o avaliar\\u00e1 a entrada desse novo piloto, podendo vetar a participa\\u00e7\\u00e3o deste.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><br \\/>2.3.2) Caso o piloto seja aprovado pela comiss\\u00e3o, ele assumir\\u00e1 os pontos e puni\\u00e7\\u00f5es do piloto substitu\\u00eddo.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>2.3.3) Caso o piloto n\\u00e3o indique outro para seu lugar, a comiss\\u00e3o reserva o direito de n\\u00e3o devolver o valor da inscri\\u00e7\\u00e3o pago, ficando o piloto obrigado a pagar at\\u00e9 o m\\u00eas da desist\\u00eancia.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>2.5) N\\u00c3O SERA PERMITIDO A PARTICIPA\\u00c7\\u00c3O DE CONVIDADOS NO CAMPEONATO<br \\/> <br \\/>2.6) Os karts a serem utilizados no campeonato das categorias FAST e FURIOUS ser\\u00e3o o SUPERKART, podendo, por\\u00e9m, em casos fortuitos ou de for\\u00e7a maior, ser utilizado o kart indoor.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>2.7) Aqueles pilotos que tiverem participado das 11 etapas do campeonato, n\\u00e3o pagar\\u00e1 a 12\\u00aa etapa.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2023-02-08 17:31:46\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2024-01-30 14:08:59\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2024-01-30 13:59:52\",\"publish_up\":\"2023-02-08 17:31:46\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":12,\"ordering\":\"1\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"90\",\"metada