(190, 15, 1, '', '2024-01-30 14:28:28', 676, 2742, 'cdda21d83ea8eca98c580b2b69e01eaab8f91571', '{\"id\":15,\"asset_id\":\"95\",\"title\":\"BRIEFING\",\"alias\":\"premiacao\",\"introtext\":\"<p>6.1) No dia da corrida os pilotos devem chegar ao kart\\u00f3dromo no m\\u00ednimo com 30 (trinta) minutos de anteced\\u00eancia ao hor\\u00e1rio previsto para o in\\u00edcio da corrida.\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>6.2) Est\\u00e1 previsto o in\\u00edcio do briefing da corrida com 30 minutos antes da largada.\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">6.2.1) O piloto deve estar inscrito na corrida at\\u00e9 o final da pesagem e sorteio dos KARTS. Quem chegar ap\\u00f3s o in\\u00edcio do briefing, mesmo que esteja nas depend\\u00eancias do kart\\u00f3dromo, ir\\u00e1 largar da \\u00faltima posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o de sua categoria. Caso mais de 1 piloto se atrasar, a posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o ser\\u00e1 pela ordem de chegada a partir da \\u00faltima posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o do grid.\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>6.3) Os Karts ser\\u00e3o definidos por SORTEIO no briefing que antecede a corrida. O sorteio ser\\u00e1 realizado pelo diretor de prova juntamente com a equipe do kart\\u00f3dromo.\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2024-01-30 14:28:28\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2024-01-30 14:27:49\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":12,\"ordering\":\"15\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"373\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0),
(191, 15, 1, '', '2024-01-30 14:30:04', 676, 3770, 'a9c1cad4cca5c82c05df3a21a8723a9e85540496', '{\"id\":15,\"asset_id\":\"95\",\"title\":\"BRIEFING\",\"alias\":\"premiacao\",\"introtext\":\"<p>6.1) No dia da corrida os pilotos devem chegar ao kart\\u00f3dromo no m\\u00ednimo com 30 (trinta) minutos de anteced\\u00eancia ao hor\\u00e1rio previsto para o in\\u00edcio da corrida.\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>6.2) Est\\u00e1 previsto o in\\u00edcio do briefing da corrida com 30 minutos antes da largada.\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\\"padding-left: 30px;\\\">6.2.1) O piloto deve estar inscrito na corrida at\\u00e9 o final da pesagem e sorteio dos KARTS. Quem chegar ap\\u00f3s o in\\u00edcio do briefing, mesmo que esteja nas depend\\u00eancias do kart\\u00f3dromo, ir\\u00e1 largar da \\u00faltima posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o de sua categoria. Caso mais de 1 piloto se atrasar, a posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o ser\\u00e1 pela ordem de chegada a partir da \\u00faltima posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o do grid.\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>6.3) Os Karts ser\\u00e3o definidos por SORTEIO no briefing que antecede a corrida. O sorteio ser\\u00e1 realizado pelo diretor de prova juntamente com a equipe do kart\\u00f3dromo.\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>7) Grid, Classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o e Largada:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>7.1) O grid das Etapas 1, 6, 7 e 8 ser\\u00e3o definidos por super pole, e o Grid das etapas 2, 3, 4, 5, 9, 10, 11 e 12 ser\\u00e1 inverso a posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o do campeonato do semestre relativo a etapa.<br \\/>7.1.1) A largada ser\\u00e1 em movimento e em fila DUPLA.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>7.2) N\\u00e3o ser\\u00e1 permitido ao piloto, em hip\\u00f3tese alguma, fazer qualquer tipo de regulagem, ou altera\\u00e7\\u00e3o no kart que o piloto receber no sorteio tanto com o kart parado quanto em movimento. A \\u00fanica regulagem autorizada \\u00e9 a da posi\\u00e7\\u00e3o de banco, qualquer outra, somente poder\\u00e1 ser efetuada pelos mec\\u00e2nicos da pista; Exceto se houver algum problema no kart.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>8) Troca de Kart:<br \\/>8.1) A troca de Kart est\\u00e1 permitida, sendo o piloto obrigado a sair com o Kart do parque fechado e retornar com ele para a troca. E o mesmo ter\\u00e1 que largar dos boxes no parque fechado ap\\u00f3s os demais pilotos passarem pela curva 1.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2024-01-30 14:30:04\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2024-01-30 14:29:07\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":13,\"ordering\":\"15\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"373\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0),
(192, 21, 1, '', '2024-01-30 14:30:49', 676, 5189, '417e51acd36a5c918ac43357b39c6aa4f02f5f05', '{\"id\":21,\"asset_id\":\"101\",\"title\":\"7. PUNI\\u00c7\\u00d5ES\",\"alias\":\"punicoes\",\"introtext\":\"<p>9.1) N\\u00e3o ter\\u00e1 recurso sobre as puni\\u00e7\\u00f5es aplicadas pelo Kart\\u00f3dromo.<br \\/>9.2) N\\u00e3o ter\\u00e1 analise de v\\u00eddeo para retirada de puni\\u00e7\\u00e3o nem aplica\\u00e7\\u00e3o de puni\\u00e7\\u00e3o. A decis\\u00e3o do kart\\u00f3dromo \\u00e9 soberana no quesito puni\\u00e7\\u00e3o.<br \\/>9.3) O piloto que receber uma advert\\u00eancia (bandeira preta e branca) ser\\u00e1 punido com a perda de 5 posi\\u00e7\\u00f5es na classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o final da corrida e essa n\\u00e3o poder\\u00e1 ser usada como descarte. n\\u00e3o havendo possibilidade de recurso para esse tipo de penalidade. <br \\/>9.4) O piloto que receber duas advert\\u00eancias (bandeira preta e branca) na mesma etapa ser\\u00e1 desclassificado da corrida e esta n\\u00e3o poder\\u00e1 ser usada como descarte. n\\u00e3o havendo possibilidade de recurso para esse tipo de penalidade. <br \\/>9.5) O piloto que n\\u00e3o se apresentar utilizando a camisa oficial 2024 do SPEEDKART, receber\\u00e1 a puni\\u00e7\\u00e3o de 5 pontos na etapa. <br \\/>9.6) Haver\\u00e1 uma puni\\u00e7\\u00e3o de 05 (cinco) pontos, em cada prova que o piloto correr sem a devida identifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o; para n\\u00e3o perder os pontos os pilotos dever\\u00e3o se identificar com nome VIS\\u00cdVEL no macac\\u00e3o, capacete ou com a camisa do SPEEDKART. <br \\/>9.7) O piloto que derrubar os cones colocados para sinalizar a passagem da largada ou instalados para sinaliza\\u00e7\\u00e3o na pista receber\\u00e1 uma puni\\u00e7\\u00e3o de 5 (cinco) pontos. <br \\/>9.8) Caso algum piloto se sinta prejudicado na corrida por algum oponente este, por sua vez, dever\\u00e1 procurar a comiss\\u00e3o disciplinar e relatar o ocorrido, registrando a reclama\\u00e7\\u00e3o formalmente por escrito (via whatsapp ou e-mail). A comiss\\u00e3o ir\\u00e1 analisar a reclama\\u00e7\\u00e3o, consultando os envolvidos e os poss\\u00edveis testemunhos de outros pilotos. Caso confirmado, ser\\u00e1 aplicado uma advert\\u00eancia nos pilotos envolvidos.<br \\/>9.9) O piloto que queimar a largada, realizar a ultrapassagem ou sair da linha antes da passagem pela linha de partida ser\\u00e1 punido com 05 (cinco) posi\\u00e7\\u00f5es no resultado da corrida. <br \\/>9.10) O piloto que for flagrado saindo com as 4 rodas para fora das faixas de delimita\\u00e7\\u00e3o da pista, para obter vantagem em ultrapassagens, ser\\u00e1 penalizado em 5 (cinco) posi\\u00e7\\u00f5es no resultado da corrida. Exceto quando o kart da frente estiver rodando ou danificado. <br \\/>9.11) N\\u00e3o \\u00e9 permitido ao piloto ficar mudando de faixa para impedir a ultrapassagem. \\u00c9 permitido o m\\u00e1ximo 2 mudan\\u00e7as de faixa, sendo a \\u00faltima se for necess\\u00e1rio para tomada de curva. O piloto flagrado nesta conduta ser\\u00e1 punido com 05 (cinco) posi\\u00e7\\u00f5es no resultado da corrida. <br \\/>9.12) Por ter o esp\\u00edrito amig\\u00e1vel e saud\\u00e1vel, n\\u00e3o ser\\u00e3o toleradas condutas agressivas ou ofensas verbais. Ser\\u00e1 aplicado um a puni\\u00e7\\u00e3o de 60 (sessenta) pontos para cada ocorr\\u00eancia. Em casos extremos, com concord\\u00e2ncia de maioria simples dos pilotos, os envolvidos ser\\u00e3o convidados a sa\\u00edrem do campeonato. Sem direito a qualquer ressarcimento.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>9.13) Nas etapas de endurance ser\\u00e3o aplicadas as regras do kart\\u00f3dromo;<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>https:\\/\\/rbcracing.com.br\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/11\\/REGULAMENTO-ENDURANCE-210KM.pdf<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2024-01-30 14:30:49\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2024-01-30 14:30:13\",\"publish_up\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":15,\"ordering\":\"9\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"503\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', 0),
(193, 14, 1, '', '2024-01-30 14:33:37', 676, 3225, 'c5da1147f41fa008a860f9bb7bfea35d8abd1268', '{\"id\":14,\"asset_id\":\"94\",\"title\":\"DISPOSI\\u00c7\\u00d5ES GERAIS\",\"alias\":\"disposicoes-gerais\",\"introtext\":\"<p>10.1) Os candidatos interessados em participar do campeonato dever\\u00e3o solicitar a inscri\\u00e7\\u00e3o pr\\u00e9via no site do campeonato SPEEDKART \\u2013 <u>SPEEDKART.com.br<\\/u><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>10.2) O campeonato ter\\u00e1, no m\\u00e1ximo, 40 pilotos por categoria. A ordem de inscri\\u00e7\\u00e3o ser\\u00e1 pela data e hora da solicita\\u00e7\\u00e3o.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a010.2.1)Ap\\u00f3s esgotado o n\\u00famero de vagas, ser\\u00e1 aberto a lista de espera em ordem idem acima.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a0 \\u00a010.2.2)A confirma\\u00e7\\u00e3o da inscri\\u00e7\\u00e3o ser\\u00e1 feita ap\\u00f3s efetuado \\u00e0 comiss\\u00e3o organizadora, o pagamento a do valor da inscri\\u00e7\\u00e3o do campeonato.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0O piloto que estiver inadimplente com o pagamento da inscri\\u00e7\\u00e3o do campeonato n\\u00e3o ter\\u00e1 seus pontos computados na classifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o do campeonato.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0Para esclarecimento de d\\u00favidas sobre esse regulamento, favor entrar em contato com a comiss\\u00e3o organizadora que \\u00e9 formada pelos seguintes membros:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Leo Marx<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Islander Lisboa (Dinho)<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Marcio Vasconcelos<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Chico<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Fernando Mota<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Este regulamento estrar\\u00e1 em vigor no dia 01\\/01\\/2024 e ter\\u00e1 sua vig\\u00eancia at\\u00e9 o final da temporada.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"9\",\"created\":\"2018-01-04 18:56:08\",\"created_by\":\"676\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2024-01-30 14:33:37\",\"modified_by\":\"676\",\"checked_out\":\"676\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2024-01